(13, 'in-the-agenda', 'pressrelease/agenda/thumbnail.jpg', 'pressrelease/agenda/header.jpg', 'cebudoc, healthful, in the agenda, scoliosis awareness day, big latch on, labor day medical mission, team operation smile, cebu doctors university hospital 46th anniversary, run for sight foundation, top taxpayers', 'In The Agenda', 'Scoliosis Awareness Day is an advocacy of an independently organized group Scoliosis Philippines that CebuDoc supported through organizing Scoliosis Awareness Week for Visayas offering free scoliosis screening and discounts on X-ray services. 124 Participants were screened for free All year ‘round, we run advocacy campaigns, community outreach activities and events in line with CebuDoc Group’s aim to reach out to more patients wherever they are. Here’s a list of what transpired few months earlier.', '<div class=\"media-container-row\">\r\n    <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style display-7\">\r\n        \r\n        Scoliosis Awareness Day is an advocacy of an independently organized group Scoliosis Philippines that CebuDoc supported through organizing Scoliosis Awareness Week for Visayas offering free scoliosis screening and discounts on X-ray services. 124 Participants were screened for free All year ‘round, we run advocacy campaigns, community outreach activities and events in line with CebuDoc Group’s aim to reach out to more patients wherever they are. Here’s a list of what transpired few months earlier.<br><br>\r\n\r\n        <ol>\r\n            <li>\r\n                SCOLIOSIS AWARENESS DAY for possible scoliosis while 21 joined the Aqua Yoga for Scoliosis patients.<br>\r\n                <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/1.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li><br>\r\n            <li>\r\n                BIG LATCH ON<br>\r\n                CebuDoc Group supports Big Latch On - a program of the Department of Health that promotes breastfeeding for mothers, which CebuDoc and its affiliate hospitals actively participate every year. 400+ mothers with their babies joined the breastfeeding activity.<br>\r\n                <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/2.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\"  alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li><br>\r\n            <li>\r\n                LABOR DAY MEDICAL MISSION<br>\r\n                Labor Day Medical Mission is a Department of Labor and Employment initiative last May 2018 that CebuDoc supported by providing volunteers to do nutrition counseling, circumcision, pharmacy dispensing and nursing the patients.<br>\r\n                <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/3.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\"  alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li><br>\r\n            <li>\r\n                TEAM OPERATION SMILE<br>\r\n                With the same commitment to serve the people, Dr. Bill Magee, the Co-founder & CEO of Operation Smile, personally flew over to Cebu to discuss with Dr. Yong Larrazabal their future endeavor to help more children with cleft lip and palate. A Medical Mission in NorthGen renewed the hope of children with cleft lip and palate. With the help of MSY Charitable Foundation Inc., and over a hundred of medical and non-medical Chinese and Filipino volunteers, free consultation and operation were served for the children.<br>\r\n                <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/4.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\"  alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li><br>\r\n            <li>\r\n                Cebu Doctors University Hospital celebrates its 46th Anniversary! Together, we’ll continue to deliver compassionate service, continuous innovation, and the best quality healthcare for our patients. Among those recognized were service awardees and perfect attendance awardees.<br>\r\n                <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/5.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\"  alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li><br>\r\n            <li>\r\n                 RUN FOR SIGHT FOUNDATION<br>\r\n                 Cebu Doc supports Run for Sight foundation by actively participating on the 13th University Run whose proceeds will help victims of calamities and beneficiaries of Run for Sight Foundation.<br>\r\n                 <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/6.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\"  alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li><br>\r\n            <li>\r\n                TOP TAXPAYERS<br>\r\n                NorthGen and SouthGen were awarded top business taxpayers by their respective local government units (LGUs). The awards were given by the respective mayors of Cebu City and the City of Naga.<br>\r\n                <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease/agenda/7.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 300px\"  alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n            </li>\r\n\r\n        </ol>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>', '', 'February 18, 2019', 'community');
