(6, 'Cebudoc-Dental-Institute', 'pressrelease_new/dental/thumbnail-2000x1328-800x531.jpg', 'pressrelease_new/dental/thumbnail-2000x1328.jpg', 'cebudoc, healthful, mactan doctors hospital, Bright smile at the Cebudoc Dental Institute', 'Cebudoc Dental Institute', 'COMPLEMENTING CEBUDOC’S GROWING BRAND OF WELLNESS CONCEPTS CONCEPTS, the CebuDoc Dental Institute ', ' <div class=\"container\">         <div class=\"media-container-row\">             <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-12\">                 <div class=\"\">                   <div class=\"col-12 mbr-fonts-style  display-7 col-md-12\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                     <p>                        COMPLEMENTING CEBUDOC’S GROWING BRAND OF WELLNESS CONCEPTS, the CebuDoc Dental Institute offers a comprehensive and advanced array of dental health services such as General Dentistry, Preventive Dentistry, Dental Diagnostic Laboratory Services, Orthodontics, Endodontics, Cosmetic Dentistry, Prosthodontics, Pediatric Dentistry, TMD Management, Periodontics, Dental Implants, and Oral Maxillofacial Surgery.                     </p>                      <p>                         The newly built dental facility is part of the developing Wellness Complex situated in the Medical Arts Building 2 of Cebu Doctors University Hospital. It is the second center opened since Wellness Complex has been introduced last year through the opening of the Center for Aesthetics and Laser.                     </p>                      <p>                        “We have been investing to change the healthcare system in CebuDoc Group which we want to provide a holistic type of care and this is part of it, the dental healthcare system,” said CebuDoc Group’s President and Chairman, Dr. Potenciano “Yong” Larrazabal, III.                     </p>                      <p>                         <h3>                             Authority in Dental Health                         </h3>                         This latest wellness brand of CebuDoc Group boasts authority in the dental health industry having gathered the most reputable and topcaliber dentists in the region headed by its chairman, Dr. Imelda P. Montuerto, who is also the current Dean of Cebu Doctors University College of Dentistry.                      </p>                     <p>                         “Here in our dental center, we made sure that all our staff is very compassionate that will attend to your every need. We’ve chosen and we’ve got top-notch dentists all under one roof – they are very known and highly regarded in their respective fields of dentistry,” Dr. Larrazabal emphasized.                     </p>                      <p>                       Joining the team are Dr. Charles P. Sia who specializes in Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery, Dr. Andrea A. Arancillo in Periodontics & Implant Dentistry, Dr. Sandra G. Lavastilla and Dr. Zonnette M. Enso in Endodontics, Dr. Larissa Ann A. Lim in Pediatric Dentistry, Dr. Joanna Bless T. Yap in Orthodontics, and Dr. Judy Melissa L. Vesuña and Dr. Jestoni D. Lagare in General Dentistry.                     </p>                      <p>                       <h3>Leader in Innovation</h3>                       Known for its innovative brands, CebuDoc Dental Institute is equipped with the latest technology in Dental Wellness that will make the patient experience more reliable and digitally integrated.                     </p>                     <p>                         “We are known to innovate. Whatever is new in the industry, we provide. Our dental center has a CBCT (Cone Beam Computed Tomography) or CT-Scan for Dentists which has a digitalized X-Ray System, we have 3 dental chairs, and one operating room,” Dr. Larrazabal added.                      </p>                     <p>                         “It will not only be an ordinary dental clinic because eventually we will be offering residency program in the different dental specializations,” said CebuDoc Dental Institute Chairman, Dr. Imelda Montuerto.                     </p>                     <div class=\"card-img \">                         <div class=\"testimonials-item\">                             <div class=\"user row\">                               <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">                                 <div class=\"user_image\">                                   <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/dental/10-1-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" class=\"\">                                 </div>                               </div>                               <div class=\"testimonials-caption col-lg-6 col-md-6\">                                <div class=\"align-left \">                                    <p class=\"\"></p><h4 class=\"mbr-title mbr-font-style display-11\">Binibining Cebu 2018 Queens</h4> <p class=\"\"></p>                                    <ul style=\"text-align: left;\">                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Yong Larrazabal III</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Andrea Arancillo</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Sandra Lavastilla</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Jestoni Lagari</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Joanne Bless Yap</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Judy Melissa Vesuña</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Zonnette M. Enso</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Charles Sia</a></li>                                        <li class=\"\"><a class=\"\">Dr. Imelda Montuerto</a></li>                                    </ul>                                 </div>                             </div>                         </div>                     </div>                 </div>      