(8, 'Full-Steam-ahead-with-OrmocDocs-New-CT-Scan', 'pressrelease_new/ormocdoc/thumbnail.jpg', 'pressrelease_new/ormocdoc/thumbnail.jpg', 'cebudoc, healthful, Full Steam ahead with OrmocDoc\'s New CT Scan', 'Full Steam ahead with OrmocDoc\'s New CT Scan', 'The CDG and OrmocDoc officials with Ormoc City Mayor Hon. Richard Gomez ', ' <div class=\"container\">         <div class=\"media-container-row\">             <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-12\">                                 <h3 class=\" align-center pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\">                     The CDG and OrmocDoc                     officials with Ormoc                     City Mayor Hon. Richard Gomez.                 </h3>                 <br>                 <div class=\"\">                     <div class=\"col-12 mbr-fonts-style  display-7 col-md-12\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                         <p>                           ORMOC DOCTORS HOSPITAL, THE LEADER IN HEALTHCARE INNOVATION IN ORMOC and one of the fastest developing hospitals of CebuDoc Group has acquired cuttingedge radiologic technology—the Philips Access Computed Tomography (CT) Scan.                         </p>                          <p>                           “In line with CebuDoc Group’s mission to provide compassionate, high-quality, and innovative healthcare service, OrmocDoc is moving forward together with other member hospitals of the group in providing technology advancement for our patients,” said Engr. Hilario Jake Cortes, OrmocDoc Hospital Administrator.                         </p>                          <p>                           OrmocDoc’s new CT Scan provides extensive patient care and gives the medical staff the ability to perform low dose scans using iterative reconstruction iDose.                         </p>                          <p>                             The Philips Access CT Scan can perform majority of scans in a single breadth hold and has an improved and wider coverage of images for more accurate results at a reasonably low cost.                         </p>                         <p>                           “Our new CT Scan has a faster scanning time which is 0.7 seconds per rotation which was not possible previously. Indeed, things just got better in OrmocDoc,” said Mr. Ian Laping, Chief RadTech in OrmocDoc.                         </p>                         <p>                             <h3>                             We are at your service!                             </h3>                             For questions and inquiries<br>                             please call OrmocDoc at (053) 255 7522<br>                             local 109 or email                              <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:blue !important;\">ormocdoc@cebudocgroup.com.</a>                         </p>                     </div>                 </div>             </div>         </div>     </div>', ' <div class=\"container\">         <div><!-- Filter --><!-- Gallery --><div class=\"mbr-gallery-row\"><div class=\"mbr-gallery-layout-default\"><div><div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"0\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/ormocdoc/gallery/3-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/ormocdoc/gallery/4-1-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/orm