(9, 'A-Haven-for-Wellness', 'pressrelease_new/wellness/thumbnail.jpg', 'pressrelease_new/wellness/thumbnail.jpg', 'cebudoc, healthful, A Haven for Wellness', 'A Haven for Wellness', 'NorthGen launches first private hospital-based CDCare in VisMin A STRESS-FREE ENVIRONMENT where one can experience ', '<div class=\"container\">        <div class=\"media-container-row\">            <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-12\">                <h3 class=\" align-center pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\">                   NorthGen launches first private hospital-based CDCare in VisMin                </h3>                <br>                <div class=\"\">                    <div class=\"col-12 mbr-fonts-style  display-7 col-md-12\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                        <p>                          A STRESS-FREE ENVIRONMENT where one can experience peace and harmony while recuperating This is what North General Hospital in Talamban, Cebu City offers to patients on its 17th anniversary as it launched the Chemical Dependents Control and Rehabilitation Center (CDCare), the first facility of its kind in Visayas and Mindanao.                        </p>                        <p>                          The center features a 48- bed facility with amenities such as a library, multi-purpose halls, detoxification rooms, among others. It also has private and semi-private accommodation and medical wards.                        </p>                        <p>                          Staffed with a well-rounded team of psychiatrists, psychologists, and nurses, CDCare is positioned to be a temporary shelter intended to reform drug offenders and members of society that need mental aid.                        </p>                        <p>                            “Our programs are the main strength of the facility. We have comprehensive, continuum, and individualized programs for the patients. NorthGen CDCare is a DOH-licensed and accredited rehabilitation center for chemical dependents’ rehabilitation,” said Manuel Delos Santos, CDCare Program Director.                        </p>                        <p>                          “In here, we provide utmost services as well as an ideal environment to our patients to help them recover faster,” said Dr. Maria Janet S. Porcia, NorthGen Medical Director.                        </p>                        <div class=\"card-img\" style=\"width: 50%\">                           <div class=\"mbr-gallery-row \">                                <div class=\"mbr-gallery-layout-default\">                                    <div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Awesome\">                                        <div href=\"#lb-gallery1-p\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-toggle=\"modal\">                                            <img src=\"<?php echo base_url();?>images/stories/cdhg1.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" class=\"\">                                        </div>                                   </div>                                </div>                                                            </div>                        </div>                         <p>Recreation area at NorthGen’s CDCare</p>                        <p>                            <h3>                             Contact CDCare at NorthGen                            </h3>                            For inquiries on NorthGen CDCare and other information,<br>                            please call (032) 343-7777<br>                            local 109 or email                            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color:blue !important;\">northgen@cebudocgroup.com.</a>                        </p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>', '<div class=\"container\">        <div><!-- Filter --><!-- Gallery --><div class=\"mbr-gallery-row\"><div class=\"mbr-gallery-layout-default\"><div><div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--