(13, 'fast-facts-about-ormocdoc', 'pressrelease/factsaboutormoc/thumbnail.jpg', 'pressrelease/factsaboutormoc/header.jpg', 'cebudoc, healthful, Fast Facts about OrmocDoc', 'Fast Facts about OrmocDoc', '1. Ormoc City is the hometown of the late Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal Jr. The hospital stands beside his family’s', '<div class=\"media-container-row\">     <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style display-7\">         <ol>             <li class=\"\">                 <strong>Ormoc City</strong> is the hometown of the late <strong>Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal Jr.</strong><br>                 The hospital stands beside his family’s ancestral home.             </li>             <li class=\"\">                 OrmocDoc offered <strong>scholarships to deserving students</strong> in the Medical and Healthcare fields in Region 8.             </li>             <li class=\"\">                 OrmocDoc is the only hospital with Operational Pulmonary Department with <strong>4 Registered Respiratory Technicians</strong> in Ormoc.             </li>             <li class=\"\">                 OrmocDoc has <strong>18 outpatient clinics</strong>, which houses the largest collection of medical doctors in one location in Ormoc City. It also has <strong>77 private rooms and 67 ward rooms.</strong>             </li>             <li class=\"\">                 OrmocDoc has the largest <strong>Level 3 hospital pharmacy</strong> in Ormoc City that is open 24/7 offering easy access to medications.             </li>             <li class=\"\">                 Inaugurated on <strong>October 28, 2012</strong>, OrmocDoc is the youngest hospital among the CDG family.             </li>             <li class=\"\">                 <strong>Passive cooling</strong> was incorporated in the building design to lower heat at the hallways without energy consumption.             </li>         </ol>     </div> </div>', '', '', 'Profiles'),
