(15, 'CebuDoc-hosts-the-Santo-Nino-de-Cebu', 'pressrelease_new/stonino/thumbnail.jpg', 'pressrelease_new/stonino/thumbnail.jpg', 'Cebudoc, Healthful, CebuDoc hosts the Santo Niño de Cebu', 'CebuDoc hosts the Santo Niño de Cebu', 'CEBU DOCTORS UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL WAS OFF TO A BLESSED START THIS YEAR because of a very important first-time visitor in January: the image of the Sto. Niño de Cebu. The visit of the Holy Child was part of the activities for the Sinulog festivities, which ', '<div class=\"container\">         <div class=\"media-container-row\">             <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-12\">                 <div class=\"\">                     <div class=\"col-12 mbr-fonts-style  display-7 col-md-12\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                         <p>                           CEBU DOCTORS UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL WAS OFF TO A BLESSED START THIS YEAR because of a very important first-time visitor in January: the image of the Sto. Niño de Cebu. The visit of the Holy Child was part of the activities for the Sinulog festivities, which included the nine-day masses leading up to the 454th Fiesta Señor celebration last January 20, 2019.                         </p>                          <p>                           The CebuDoc community warmly welcomed the miraculous image, with several personnel turning emotional and shedding tears as they thanked God for all the blessings and prayed for physical and spiritual healing.                          </p>                          <p>                           “I am happy that CebuDoc is one of the places visited by the Sto. Niño, especially for the patients who could not attend the Sinulog because of their health conditions,” said Sr. Ma. Leonora D. Se-it, LGC Pastoral Coordinator. The image of the Señor Santo Niño de Cebu was displayed at CebuDoc Chapel and stayed for an overnight vigil.                           </p>                                               </div>                 </div>             </div>         </div>     </div>', '<div class=\"container\">         <div><!-- Filter --><!-- Gallery --><div class=\"mbr-gallery-row\"><div class=\"mbr-gallery-layout-default\"><div><div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"0\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/stonino/gallery/dsc0370-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/stonino/gallery/dsc0378-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/stonino/gallery/dsc0422-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"3\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/stonino/gallery/dsc0369-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"clearfix\"></div></div></div><!-- Lightbox --><div data-app-prevent-settings=\"\" class=\"mbr-slider modal fade carousel slide\" tabindex=\"-1\" data-keyboard=\"true\" data-interval=\"false\" id=\"lb-gallery1-h\"><div class=\"modal-dialog\"><div class=\"modal-content\"><div class=\"modal-body\"><div class=\"carousel-inner\"><div class=\"carousel-item\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrel