     <center> <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style display-7 \"><strong>JEAN DOLINO</strong></h4></center>                                 <div style=\"min-height:10vh;\">                                     <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                                         <b>Receptionist, X-Ray Dept.<br></b>                                         “After 29 years of working, CebuDoc has become a family to me. I have seen students become interns, interns become residents and residents become consultants.”                                     </p>                                 </div>                             </div>                         </div>                     </div>                      <!--Card-5-->                     <div class=\"card col-12 col-md-6 p-3 col-lg-4\" id=\"MELVIN\">                         <div class=\"card-wrapper\">                             <div class=\"card-img \">                                 <img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/work-cdg/melvin.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">                             </div>                             <div class=\"card-box mt-3\">                                 <center> <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style display-7\"><strong>MELVIN DENIEGA</strong></h4></center>                                 <div style=\"min-height:11.5vh;\">                                     <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                                         <b>Assistant Head, Financial                                         Management Section<br></b>                                         “I learned a lot from working here in CebuDoc for 9 years. I live and work in an environment that is well-balanced.”                                    </p>                                 </div>                             </div>                         </div>                     </div>                     <!--Card-5-->                