(17, 'Dr-Manuel-Lim', 'pressrelease_new/profile1-600x400.png', 'pressrelease_new/profile1-600x400.png', 'cebudoc, Healthful, Dr. Manuel Lim', 'Dr. Manuel Lim', 'BRILLIANT MIND,COMPASSIONATE HEART\r\n\r\n“YOU MAY BE THE BEST DOCTOR IN THE WORLD BUT IF YOU ARE NOT ACCESSIBLE, WHAT GOOD ARE YOU?” This quote pretty much sums up Dr. Manuel Lim’s principle when it comes to his life mission of providing the best medical care to his patients.\r\n\r\nDr. Lim started the Coronary Care Unit and Cebu Cardiovascular Surgery Center, making treatment more accessible to Cebuanos as they no longer had to fly to Manila to seek medical attention. ', '        <div class=\"container\">             <div class=\"media-container-row\">                 <div class=\"title col-12 col-md-9\">                      <h3 class=\" align-center pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\">BRILLIANT MIND,COMPASSIONATE HEART</h3>                 </div>             </div>                         <div class=\"media-container-row\">                 <div class=\" col-12 mbr-fonts-style  display-7 col-md-10\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                     <p>                         “YOU MAY BE THE BEST DOCTOR IN THE WORLD BUT IF YOU ARE NOT ACCESSIBLE, WHAT GOOD ARE YOU?” This quote pretty much sums up Dr. Manuel Lim’s principle when it comes to his life mission of providing the best medical care to his patients.                     </p>                      <p>                        Dr. Lim started the Coronary Care Unit and Cebu Cardiovascular Surgery Center, making treatment more accessible to Cebuanos as they no longer had to fly to Manila to seek medical attention.                     </p>                      <p>                        He says he gets that wonderful feeling of fulfillment everytime he is able to diagnose a patient’s ailment accurately and find a promising treatment.                     </p>                      <p>                         “This feeling of fulfillment keeps me going and motivates me to study and learn more,” Dr. Lim declares.                     </p>                      <p>                        The pioneering Cebuano cardiologist may have already logged decades of unparalleled service in his field of expertise but he is showing no signs of slowing down and is in fact hungrier to learn new things. Here, Dr. Lim defines work and success and gives a piece of advice to younger physicians.                     </p>                                          <div class=\"row pb-3\">                                                 <div class=\"col-lg-12 img-item item1\" style=\"width: 100%;\">                             <h3 class=\"align-left pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\"> “Every failure in my life is an inspiration for me to work harder.”</h3>                             <h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\">                                 Dr. Yong Larrazabal III presents the inaugural Potenciano V. Larrazabal Jr. Lifetime Achievement Award to Dr. Manuel Lim during the CebuDoc Group Gala and Appreciation Night                             </h3>                             <p>                                                              </p>                         </div>                     </div>                     <p>                         </p><p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> What is your definition of work?</h3>                              Work is to provide the best medical care to the sick regardless of their wealth or status. When it becomes a mission, my work becomes my life. When one loves his work, it no longer becomes work.                          <p></p>                         <p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What does success mean to you?</h3>                             Success does not happen by accident. Success is loving what you’re doing and succeeding through hard work, perseverance, learning, dedication and sacrifice.                         <p></p>                          <p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What is the secret to your success?</h3>                              Passion. And keeping that passion burning! For me, every failure in my life is an inspiration to work harder.                          <p></p>                                                  <p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What current challenges in your field excite you?</h3>                             New diseases have become more difficult to treat. However, modern treatment and drugs have improved so much, too. Learning, studying and understanding them are the challenges that continue to excite me.                          <p></p>                                                  <p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What is the best career decision you’ve ever made?</h3>                             To train at Cook County Hospital in Chicago and to come home to Cebu to practice.                                                  <p></p>                                                  <p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What impact do you want to have on other people’s lives?</h3>                             As a doctor, I hope that my years of passionate practice will inspire young physicians to pursue work ethics that looks at the patients’ well-being and care as the motivating force for them to be the best.                          <p></p>                                                  <p>                             </p><h3 class=\"align-left mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What is your advice to younger doctors?</h3>                             Find their own specialization and once they’ve found it, seek a good training program to be among the best.                         <p></p>                     <p></p>                 </div>             </div>         </div>', '', '', 'Profiles'),
