(18, 'cebudoc-sportsfest', 'pressrelease_new/sportsfest/dsc1178-2000x1328-800x531.jpg', 'pressrelease_new/sportsfest/-dsc1178-2000x1328.jpg', 'cebudoc, healthful, CebuDoc Sportsfest', 'CebuDoc Sportsfest', 'Let the Games Begin!\r\n\r\nTO PROMOTE SYNERGY IN THE HOSPITAL, CebuDoc employees gathered around Medical Arts Building 1 to officially open CebuDoc SportsFest 2019 with the theme: “Building camaraderie with fun and fitness through sports.” ', '<div class=\"p-0 ml-2 col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12\">                             <div class=\"card-box\">                                 <div class=\"mbr-fonts-style display-7\" style=\"font-size:1em;\">                                     <p>                                         TO PROMOTE SYNERGY IN THE HOSPITAL, CebuDoc employees gathered around Medical Arts Building 1 to officially open CebuDoc SportsFest 2019 with the theme: “Building camaraderie with fun and fitness through sports.”                                     </p>                                     <p>                                         The SportsFest events included a footparade, awarding of muses and the start of the ball tournament, which included basketball and volleyball games.                                    </p>                                      <p>                                         Making a comeback this year, the SportsFest ran for the entire month of July until August 18, in line with the celebration of CebuDoc Group’s 47th Founding Anniversary. This year saw its largest turnout yet, motivating the teams to play harder and making the games more exciting.                                     </p>                                      <p>                                         “The SportsFest this year was really nice because there was unity and every team had its own cheer. We really enjoyed watching, and you can feel the closeness and bonding among the staff plus the full support coming from each department,” said Ms. Pretzel Maghanoy, an HR staff.                                     </p>                                      <p>                                           The CebuDoc SporstFest has always fostered stronger relationships among its participants. It’s all in the spirit of fun while friendly competition and teamwork bring out the best in each player.                                     </p>                                                                     </div>                             </div>                         </div>', '<div class=\"container\">         <div><!-- Filter --><!-- Gallery --><div class=\"mbr-gallery-row\"><div class=\"mbr-gallery-layout-default\"><div><div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"0\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/sportsfest/dsc0952-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/sportsfest/dsc1178-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-h\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets_healthful/images/pressrelease_new/sportsfest/dsc0951-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"clearfix\"></div></div></div><!-- Lightbox --><div data-app-prevent-settings=\"\" class=\"mbr-slider modal fade carousel slide\" tabindex=\"-1\" data-keyboard=\"true\" data-interval=\"false\" id=\"lb-gallery1-h\"><div class=\"modal-dialog\"><div class=\"modal-content\"><