(17, 'Aldwin Narido Ybanez', '8482204659', 'aldwinybanez@gmail.com', 'North Carolina', 'US', 'hr', 'Verification of Employment Dates', 'Please provide me with my employment dates for my resume which is needed for my employment here in North Carolina. I need the start date and end date of my employment.\n\nLooking forward to your response. Thank you very much and I really appreciate your time.', '08/16/2014 01:36:09 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(19, 'Matiola L. Villanueva', '639154270102', 'villanueva.ml07@gmail.com', 'Ormoc City', 'PH', 'info', 'August 20 (Women Clinic Open)', 'Dear Ma\'am / Sir,\n\nGood afternoon!\n\nI would like to inquire if your women clinic open will be open on August 20, 2014 and the availability of the radiologist. Since this month will be my annual sonomammogram with Dr Christine Esther Leonardia-Suarez your radiologist.\n\nAppreciate to receive a reply the soonest for my preparation of travel to Cebu City. Thank you so much.', '08/18/2014 01:10:57 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(21, 'Efren Ll. Cruz', '0917-505-0709', 'efren@personalfinance.ph', 'Quezon City', 'PH', 'hr', 'Invitation for Doctors to Attend the EnRich Estate Planning Training', 'Our training is designed to help doctors leave more for their heirs, after all it\'s theirs.  This is done by practicing income tacts approved by law through estate planning and not just leaving everything to income tax.\n\nWe are running our EnRich Estate Planning event on September 26, 2014, 1-5 pm at the SM City Cebu Megatrade Hall.  The knowledge investment is only Php1,000 per person. Then they can attend our FREE EnRich Cash, Debt, Risk and Wealth Management training.  They get to choose between two time slots, 8 am to 12 noon or 1 to 5 pm.\n\nPlease visit www.personalfinance.ph to get to know more about us.  You may also click the button Next EnRich to see our training offerings.\n\nIf you approve of our training, we can send you a poster for email blast on posting on your bulletin board.\n\nThank you for giving us the opportunity to spread the word on personal finance.\n\nVery truly yours,\n\nEfren Ll. Cruz, RFP\nChairman and CEO\nPersonal Finance Advisers Philippines Corporation', '08/21/2014 05:18:10 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(22, 'Efren Ll. Cuz, RFP', '0917-505-0709', 'efren@personalfinance.ph', 'Quezon City', 'PH', 'hr', 'Invitation for Employees to Attend the FREE EnRich Cash, Debt, Risk and Wealth Management Training', 'Our training is designed to help employees be more focused at work and at home by giving them the tools to better handle very distracting money concerns.\n\nWe are running our FREE EnRich Cash, Debt, Risk and Wealth training event on September 27, 2014, at the SM City Cebu Megatrade Hall.  Your employees get to choose between two time slots, 8 am to 12 noon or 1 to 5 pm.  \n\nPlease visit www.personalfinance.ph to get to know more about us.  You may also click the button Next EnRich to see our training offerings.\n\nIf you approve of our training, we can send you a poster for email blast on posting on your bulletin board.\n\nThank you for giving us the opportunity to spread the word on personal finance.\n\nVery truly yours,\n\nEfren Ll. Cruz, RFP\nChairman and CEO\nPersonal Finance Advisers Philippines Corporation', '08/21/2014 05:22:21 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(23, 'Per Gertzén', '0046761993082', 'per.gertzen@live.dk', 'Copenhagen', 'DK', 'hr', 'information, helpful staff', 'I hope that I can get a little information from them. I am a Danish man who has found a lovely Filipino woman on the Internet. I must be honest to say that I have to send some money to her, but I\'m having second thoughts about that person\'s identity and reele intentions. The woman\'s name is Sam Mansala Paige born 10 jan 1985 and she says that for two weeks ago has been employed as a nurse at the hospital. All I want to know is, are these details - yes or no. \nI hope for their understanding of this inquiry and look forward to receiving a response from them\n\nSincerely, Per Gertzén', '08/22/2014 01:44:20 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(25, 'fair flower mejor', '09232903061', 'mejorfair@yahoo.com', 'cebu city', 'PH', 'delivery', 'maternity cost', 'Hi\n \nGood day!\n\nI would like to inquire if I can get a quotation for how much it would cost me if I\'ll have my delivery in your hospital.. I wanna know the cost for \n1.normal delivery (private room)\n2.normal delivery (ward)\n3. C-section ( private room)\n4. C-section (ward (', '08/22/2014 11:57:23 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(26, 'Paterno', '09322074090', 'nolascokatrinamae@yahoo.com', 'cebu city', 'PH', 'info', 'good day maam', 'Im trying to gather information regarding if you have available flexible nail #1 please reply if there\' s available thank you ', '08/22/2014 08:19:02 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(30, 'Sheremae Alcantara', '09173107176', 'emmyalc04@gmail.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'info', 'magnetic resonance imaging MRI', 'Hello..my mother is terribly sick. We are advised to have her undergo MRI. I just want to inquire how much is the cost of such procedure? Also how much is the hospital admission fee? Thank you. I would really appreciate it if you will reply.\n', '08/25/2014 12:58:56 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(31, 'Sheremae Alcantara', '09173107176', 'emmyalc04@gmail.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'radiology', 'MRI', 'Hello..my mother is terribly sick and we are advised to have her undergo MRI. I just want to ask how much would the whole MRI Procedure cost? Thank you. We would really appreciate it if you will reply.', '08/25/2014 01:09:14 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(32, 'Adam Smith', '0477438172', 'adam.smithy74@gmail.com', 'Perth WA', 'AU', 'Admin', 'Patient contact', 'Hello we have been trying to contact the hospital in regard to my brother who is currently staying at your hospital. His name is Dale Anderson\nConsistently, our calls are not answered or we are hung up on. \nIt is urgent that we are contacted to be updated on my brothers condition.\nThank you.\nAdam\n', '08/25/2014 03:29:09 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(34, 'Maria Gigi O. Adonis', '09223832243', 'clin_2005@yahoo.com', 'Ormoc City', 'PH', 'radiology', 'Rate', 'mag inquire lang ko pila inyo rate sa CT scan sa lungs with contrast. thank you', '08/25/2014 06:20:17 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(44, 'Rose Hoggard', '639292414520', 'rjhoggard@yahoo.com', 'CA', 'US', 'info', 'About my mom\'s condition', 'Good day CDH,\n\nPlease Help!\nCan I ask you a few questions here about my mother\'s condition. I am here in California, so I have been worried sick for my mom. Last year of 2013, she was admitted to Ormoc Doctors Hospital by my dad and siblings because of severe stomach pain. They did blood work and ultrasound but it came out negative. They had her stay at the hospital for a couple of days for one test everyday. The results were negative and the doctor said that she has to avoid eating fatty foods because her liver looked like there are alot of fats in it. Her doctor  didn\'t give clear details about her condition so we were kind of confused until she was discharged. She had prescription for her stomach pain. These days, my siblings have been telling me that she doesn\'t look like okay like there is something she is feeling inside that she\'s not telling us. A couple of time she\'s been weak, dizzy, didn\'t eat much. And her facial expression looks like she\'s in pain. Please help, I\'m looking for a doctor who can help us and make sure she is okay. I would greatly appreciate your help and response. God bless you all. ', '09/01/2014 10:34:28 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(45, 'Cris Jovanie Muyet', '09082833745', 'gioyet2001@yahoo.com', 'Lapu-Lapu City', 'PH', 'info', 'Skin Biopsy Price', 'Good Afternoon.\n\nI would just like to ask for the price of skin biopsy. Are there any preparations that I need to know before the surgery?\n\nHoping for your positive response.\n\nThank you.', '09/01/2014 12:42:30 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(46, 'MARTIN PENFOLD', '09215324232', 'penmar51@yahoo.com', 'CEBU', 'PH', 'info', 'HEALTH INS. FOR UK EXPAT', 'I am a healthy 63 year old expat retired in Cebu,\nDoes your hospital have a healthcare plan I can pay into ?\nOr can you recommend an insurer that you recognise ?\nThankyou,\nMr Martin Penfold.', '09/03/2014 02:12:32 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(47, 'David Michael Naylor', '0639355792413', 'mrdmn_10@yahoo.co.uk', 'Dipolog City', 'PH', 'info', 'Knee Replacement', 'WithIn the last year I\'ve attended Cebu Doctors Hospital for a D2 x-ray scan and other blood tests.\n\nI now have pains in my right knee and I\'m fairly sure that I need a knee replacement. Do you preform this sort of surgery and if so what is the presedure to carry out the operation and the total cost. I\'m coming to Cebu for 3 night stay from 17th Sept.\n\nRegards', '09/03/2014 01:02:45 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(48, 'Cipriano Jr, Abatayo', '0016303986039', 'yhan_080787@yahoo.com', 'Illinois', 'US', 'info', 'Final bill inquiry', 'My mother has been hospitalised since monday 09/01/14 her name is GUILLERMA TAREGA ABATAYO. She is due to be released on saturday 09/06/14. Do you think you can give an estimate of the final bill. Or can you send the final bill to my email address please. \n\nThank you.', '09/04/2014 12:41:43 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(49, 'Brian Fraser', '09199498588', 'brianatcoffscoast1@hotmail.com', 'dumaguete', 'PH', 'info', 'do you have a Dr Mela Chan?', 'Hello I believe there is a Dr Mela Chan that works from your hospital, I am in the need of a specialist that can do artificial insemination, I have had my prostate removed due to cancer in 2009, my partner and I wish to have a baby, we both reside in Dumaguete. \nIf Dr Chan is not there maybe you could suggest or provide a list of suitable Doctors  \nThank you Brian Fraser\n', '09/05/2014 11:20:53 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(51, 'gen', '09275861936', 'bhaby.gen14@yahoo.com', 'cebu city', 'PH', 'info', 'sebaceous cyst excision cost', 'how much does it cost for the removal of sebaceous cyst? please reply. I am currently working here onboard I am a seaman and I need to have an estimate cost for this minor procedure. thank you!', '09/05/2014 09:19:58 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
