(177, 'Mohammad Anzal Rehman', '00966569514289', 'anzalrehman@hotmail.com', 'Dammam', 'SA', 'hr', 'Inquiry regarding Residency', '<p>Dear Sir/ Madam,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I am writing to request information regarding the application process for obtaining a Medical/ Surgical Residency at Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital, Philippines. I am a medical graduate from Avalon University School of Medicine, a Carribean Medical School that awarded me my M.D. degree in August of 2012. I would like to also add that, as part of my course, I undertook 72 weeks of externship at Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital from October 2010 to August 2012.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I have attached my CV for further details on my qualifications and possess several letters of recommendation from Attending Physicians at CDUH. I am also ECFMG certified by the U.S.A. However, I would like to ask whether I would be eligible to enroll in your institution and also if I will be allowed to subsequently obtain a license to work in the Philippines as a Pakistani citizen. If I am eligible, kindly send me an overview of the process which I should follow in order to apply to your prestigious establishment for a Residency position.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you very much for your time and cooperation. I fervently look forward to receiving a favorable reply as soon as is possible by you.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Regards,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Dr Mohammad Anzal Rehman&nbsp;</p>', '11/02/2014 09:33:54 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
