(256, 'Jay Mottern', '09184091635', 'motterj@gmail.com', 'Mandaue City, Cebu', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Hernia surgery cost estimate', '<p>Hello. I have an indirect inguinal hernia on my left side. I have seen Dr. Jose Uy Tan, Jr. at North Gen Hospital about it last year, and I want to have the hernia repaired soon.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I need to know about estimated costs so I can find out whether my insurance (Intellicare through the EPerformax BPO company) will cover everything or if not, how much I&#39;ll have to pay. I understand that you can&#39;t tell me the exact costs as that will depend on how the surgery goes, among other things, and that you won&#39;t be legally bound to any estimate that you give me prior to the surgery.</p><p>I want to know:</p><p>1) How much the laparoscopic surgery costs vs. the open incision surgery (in other words, what is the charge for the use of the laparoscope device), and</p><p>2) How much will a hernia mesh cost?</p><p>My insurance only covers up to P30,000 for use of a laparoscope and doesn&#39;t cover the mesh at all.</p><p>If I&#39;ve directed this message to the wrong department, kindly forward it to the correct department for me. Thanks. :)</p><p>Thank you for your time.</p><p>-Jay Mottern</p>', '12/19/2014 09:34:24 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
