(259, 'Hazen Manatad', '0507850198', 'hazenm93@yahoo.com', 'Abudhabi City', 'AE', 'info', 'Ultrasound and Mother Throat check-up', '<p>Dear Information Department,</p><p>My name is Hazen Manatad and would like to have ultrasound for my baby just to identify the gender? Can you recommend me a doctor who could see me?</p><p>Lastly, I&#39;d like to send my mother to have a whole check up, if booking ahead is a must due to availability, then I will do so. If you could recommend me a doctor??</p><p>Much appreciated.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With regards,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>HAzen</p>', '12/21/2014 08:53:12 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
