(261, 'Francis Seville', '1-201-925-4335', 'francisseville@yahoo.com', 'NJ', 'US', 'info', 'Dr. Achilles Cortes clinic hours', '<p>My mother, Mrs. Fe W. Seville had a minor operation by Dr. Achilles Cortes on Dec.10. &nbsp;She needed to see him again &amp; was told that his clinic was open on Dec.23 from 11AM - 2PM. &nbsp;My mother got there around 12noon only to find out that the clinic was already closed. &nbsp;She has no means of finding out when the clinic is open again as nobody is answering the clinic phone. &nbsp;</p><p>You can call my mother at 0915-539-8445 or my father, Judge Francisco A. Seville, Jr.&nbsp;&nbsp;at 0915-761-7151.</p><p>Hoping for a quick response from your office.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '12/24/2014 07:31:51 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
