(263, 'Paris Luckie ', '61432551044', 'Parisluckie@hotmail.com', 'New South wales ', 'AU', 'info', 'Traveller needing assistance ', '<p>Hello,&nbsp;</p><p>I am currently travelling in the Philippines and landed in Cebu yesterday. For approximately 2 days i have had pain around my right kidney radiating &nbsp;down to my groin. I believe I need to see a doctor before moving on. Am I able to present to your emergency department for treatment or another department? Please inform me of costs also. Any help would be appreciated.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Kind Regards,&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Paris Luckie&nbsp;</p>', '01/06/2015 11:53:37 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(264, 'Jovanni Ramos', '09058350368', 'jovanniramos36@gmail.com', 'Cagayan de Oro City', 'PH', 'info', 'Sputum test fee ', '<p>Good day! I am about to apply for a student visa and i want to take sputum test in advance. I have a PTB and already midicated 5 years ago. I have all my xray films. May i ask if how much is the cost of sputum test? and how long will it take?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you!&nbsp;</p>', '01/06/2015 11:20:02 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(265, 'David Husar', '9217-449995', 'david21753@hotmail.com', 'Arlington, Virginia', 'US', 'info', 'Doctor Licensing', '<p>Gentlemen:</p><p>Sorry to bother you. &nbsp;My wife and I are planning to retire to the Philippines within the next 12-18 months. &nbsp;She was born and raised in Naga and I actually worked in Cebu for the US Government from 1982-1984 and speak Cebuano. &nbsp;We currently own land on the island.&nbsp;</p><p>FYI The contact number is for my sister&nbsp;in law in Naga.</p><p>My question is this: &nbsp;Although US Medicare does not cover American retirees abroad my regular health insurance will pay claims incurred abroad. &nbsp;However for prescription drugs while I can get &nbsp;them to do &nbsp;a year at a time, I have to get the prescriptions written by a doctor licensed in the United States and I have to be &quot;seen&quot; by the doctor writing the prescription once a year under US law. &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Are any of the doctors on your staff licensed in the US and could they write the prescriptions for me? &nbsp;Barring that&nbsp;&nbsp;what is the local costs for drugs like</p><p>Atenolol</p><p>Topiramite</p><p>Dicylomine</p><p>Lomotil</p><p>Lipitor</p><p>Dexilant</p><p>Zomig</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I am perfectly willing to do generics for any and all drugs in this group.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Would I perhaps be better off getting a local health insurance policy to deal with the drug issue?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I do appreciate your time. &nbsp;I remember your facility very well. I had a motorcycle accident in 1983 and had to have surgery on my elbow in your hospital and was quite happy with the experience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thanks again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>David Husar</p>', '01/06/2015 11:42:52 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(266, 'anthony raz', '09162973015', 'anthonyraz@gmail.com', 'cebu city', 'PH', 'info', 'price package for pregnancy delivery', '<p>sir/madame</p><p>please send me a pricelist package you can offer for pregnancy delivery (normal and CS).</p><p>thank you</p>', '01/07/2015 01:04:13 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
