(275, 'Heini Hyvoenen', '00358456777407', 'heini-leena.hyvonen@metropolia.fi', 'Helsinki', 'FI', 'hr', 'Exchange students from Finland', '<p>Hello!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We are three nursing students from Metropolia University Applied Sciences from Helsinki Finland. We have been planning to do two internships (children, mental health or geriatric, depending choices of the hospital).&nbsp;</p><p>We are all already practical nurses and have been working in different kind of wards for 3-6 years (mostly internal medicine wards). Our exchange would start on 2016 spring semester.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Is there international student coordinator who we could contact in this subject and maybe get some more information and help on our project?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you! &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Best regards,&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Heini-Leena Hyv&ouml;nen, Heidi M&auml;kinen and Sara Mutta</p>', '01/12/2015 08:37:07 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(276, 'MA. GRETA QUININEZA-BALBIDO', '09272656255', 'gretaquininezabalbido@yahoo.com', 'Dampalan, Dapitan City Zamboanga del norte ', 'PH', 'info', 'DRA. DELA  CALZADA  PEDIA NEUROLOGIST', '<p>I JUST WANT TO KNOW THE CONTACT NUMBER OF DRA. DELA &nbsp;CALZADA &nbsp;PEDIA NEUROLOGIST &nbsp;FOR &nbsp;CHECK-UP &nbsp; APPOINTMENT &nbsp;OF MY SON &nbsp;REFERRED BY DRA MA. TERESA &nbsp;CABILIN-LOPEZ, M.D &nbsp;HIS PEDIATRICIAN SINCE BIRTH&nbsp; SOMEWHERE IN &nbsp;DIPOLOG &nbsp;CITY... I&#39;LL BE &nbsp;WAITING &nbsp;FOR YOUR REPLY AND THANK YOU!!!</p>', '01/14/2015 12:13:18 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
