(279, 'Charlene Kathryn Ruyeras Traces', '1-306-5011156', 'tracesc@mmm.ca', 'Regina, Saskatchewan', 'CA', 'women', 'Request for Copies of Mammogram Results', '<p>Hello,</p><p>I would like to request copies of all my mammography test results done in this Center for Women. The last mammography I had before I left for Canada and in this center was&nbsp;in 2012. I think I had&nbsp;in 2011. I&#39;m not quite sure if I had in 2010. I&#39;m currently a permanent resident of Regina, SK, Canada and I had my first mammography here in Canada just yesterday, January 13th, 2015.&nbsp;My doctor would like to see a copy my mammography result/s for their base reference.</p><p>What are you requirements to request copies of the results? Electronic copies are also okay with my doctor, as long as they can see my previous mammogram results.</p><p>Thank you so much and more power.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>Charlene Kathryn Traces<br />&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/15/2015 05:56:53 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(280, 'Paul J. & Ester M. Vollmer', '0947-346-7241', 'strtrodder49@hotmail.com', 'Clarin, Misamis Occidental', 'PH', 'info', 'Cost for a Mammogram and Possible Cost for an ENT / Audiology', '<p>I am sending this message on behalf of my wife (a former RN) who is being referred to yourselves as she has been informed that you have a very modern and efficient Mammogram Staff and modern equipment to perform the Mammogram.&nbsp; We have Caritas Health Insurance but were informed that the plan that my wife has doesn&#39;t cover annual Mammograms.&nbsp; What we are wondering is what would the cost be for a Mammogram?</p><p>I am retired U.S. Air Force and am being provided a Letter of Authorization from the Manila VA Out-Patient Clinic for an ENT / Audiology Appointment.&nbsp; So, both my wife and I can be seen by members of your staff and am unsure if I have to pay up front or if the VA will pay and then they will reimburse me, so I would like to know how this is taken care of as well.</p><p>We will be taking an overnight ferry from Ozamiz to Cebu and plan on staying (possbly) at the Best Western Hotel in close proximity to where your hotel is located.</p><p>Any information that you can provide to us (my wife) via our email or call her on her cell phone, will be appreciated as we need to make sure that we have the appropriate monetary funds (cash) in our pockets when we arrive to have her Mammogram accomplished.</p><p>Thanking you ahead of time.</p><p>Respectfully,</p><p>Paul J &amp; Ester M. Vollmer</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/15/2015 09:30:41 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
