(290, 'Paul J. & Ester M. Vollmer', '0947-346-7241', 'strtrodder49@hotmail.com', 'Clarin', 'PH', 'info', 'Fees & Appointment Information', 'To Whom It May Concern:<br />\n<br />\nWe have a couple of questions that we would like to get a response for.  They are:<br />\n<br />\na.  My wife has been approved for a visit to Cebu Doctors\' Hospital for a Mammogram.  The other day, you sent us the cost for that mammogram that she will require.  Do we need to make an appointment or do we just drop on by for her Mammogram?<br />\n<br />\nb.  I have a \"Letter of Authorization\" from the Manila VA Out-Patient Clinic for an ENT / Audiology Appointment.  Once again, do I need to make an appointment or can I just drop in and have this taken care of? <br />\n<br />\nNOTE:  Since my wife and I both have separate things to take care of at your hospital (we will be paying for her Mammogram as Caritas Health Shield (we believe) doesn\'t pay for this), we would both like to be seen the same day / date.  We plan on taking an overnight ferry from Ozamiz to Cebu and will then stay overnight(s) in a hotel close by your facility.<br />\n<br />\nc.  Can you further give us a cost breakdown of these items that Caritas Health Shield doesn\'t pay for and we will have to pay for out-of-pocket as well?  They are:<br />\n<br />\nBUN, CREATININE, HDL, HGB A1-C, PHOSPHORUS, SGOT, SGPT, TOTAL CHOLESTEROL, TOTAL PROTEIN, ALBUMIN, GLOBULIN, TRIGLYCERIDES, URIC ACID, CAROTID DOPPLER STUDIES, and 2D ECHO W/COLOR DOPPLER STUDIES.<br />\n<br />\nWe want to ensure that we have sufficient money on-hand to pay for these items that we are being asked by my wife\'s family physician - Dr Joann Lao-Go, M.D., F.P.C.P., F.P.C.C.  If you have any questions that you need to ask of her, her office phone number is:  (088) 521-2372 and her fax number is:  (088) 521-1758.<br />\n<br />\nRespectfully,<br />\n<br />\nPaul J. & Ester M. Vollmer<br />\n<br />\nP.S.  We would like to be able to be seen either the last week in January 2015 or the first week in February 2015.  So, please let us know as soon as possible so we can schedule our ferry passage and hotel accommodations.<br />\n<br />\n', '01/21/2015 08:21:29 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
