(292, 'CHIELOU T. ICBAN', '09327199261', 'chielou_26@yahoo.com', 'CEBU CITY', 'PH', 'info', 'WANT TO HAVE AN APPOINTMENT TO DR. ALTONAGA', '<p>Good day</p><p>Ako po si chielou icban may anak po akong may hydrosiphaly (developmental delay) 2yrs old</p><p>na sa kasalokoyan naka physical teraphy &amp; occupational teraphy sa vsmh, sa manila po cya nag start&nbsp; sa kanya teraphy ngayon nalipat na sa cebu.. gusto ko po cyang makita n dr. altonaga for his developmental check-up kong maari po sanang mag karoon ng cellphone number sa kanaya para makipag appointment..</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>maraming salamat po.</p>', '01/23/2015 03:50:22 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(293, 'Grace  Flor', '001161296250702', 'yhing11@yahoo.com', 'New South Wales Australia', 'AU', 'Admin', 'Regarding Hospital Bills of Era Uy', '<p>Good Morning. Im sending this letter to inquire about the full amount of hospital Bills of Era Uy who admitted in your hospital 0n 12/25/2014 due to mastectomy operation. Her room no is 441. adm no 344950. My sister in law borrowed some money on her friend to pay for the hopital bill but before sending the money to my sister inlaw glenda uy we want to know the exact amount of the hospital bills. Pls send us photo copy .</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>thank you very much for time and consideration.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>truly yours</p><p>Grace flor Uy</p>', '01/23/2015 03:54:20 pm', 'read', 'Archive');
