(295, 'Tommy Lee Tirey', '09292561847', 'sales@cebusolar.com', 'Bancasan/San Remigio', 'PH', 'Admin', 'solar power you hospital', '<p>Greetings,<br /><br />We at Cebu Solar Inc. wish to offer you solar power for any and all your buildings and home&#39;s at a price of p120 per watt.<br /><br />This is a firm offer for complete system install for systems 10 Kw and over &quot;grid-feed&quot;<br /><br />For systems with hybrid Inverter&#39;s &#39;grid-feed and battery able&quot; p130 per watt.<br /><br />any questions please call us at 0929-256-1847<br /><br />Tom Tirey<br />Gen. Manager<br />CSI<br />Philippines<br />www.cebusolar.com<br />sales@cebusolar.com<br />&nbsp;</p>', '01/24/2015 09:32:26 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
