(299, 'Jackelyn McLean', '000', 'pelaezj12@yahoo.co.uk', 'oroquita city', 'GB', 'info', 'Maxillo-Facial Surgery ( ORAL OBTURATOR )', '<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p><p>I write to you regarding possible help you could give regarding someone without an upper palate in their mouth; the person concerned has a cleft palate and is 27 years old. &nbsp;Would you be able to assess whether or not an ORAL OBTURATOR would be a possible help, without the use of surgery? &nbsp;&nbsp;We would be able to attend a clinic you wish in Cebu.</p><p>Looking forward to your help in hope.</p><p>Your faithfully,</p><p>Jackelyn Mclean</p>', '01/25/2015 09:52:58 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
