(301, 'Chenna Rose Doble', '9363085772', 'tor.steinheim@alfalaval.com', 'Bakawan', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Delivery / Ultra', '<p>Hi, i&#39;m typing this message from Norway.&nbsp; My fiancee is living in Bakawan and pregnant.&nbsp; Delivery is scheduled to midt June.</p><p>I am travelling from Norway end February /will be in Cebu on the 21st February.&nbsp; We are about to start planning for the delivery and your hospital is choosen.</p><p>Firstly, we would like to have a ultrasound once i am in Cebu, either 22 or 23rd February.&nbsp; It this possible?</p>', '01/27/2015 03:12:40 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
