(303, 'Panu Johannes Kuoppala', '358443074629', 'panu.kuoppala@netikka.fi', 'Seinajoki', 'FI', 'Admin', 'Hospital admission payment reclamation', '<p>I visited your hospital last week 22.-23.1.&nbsp;&nbsp;On arrival you took a 40000 peso deposit on my Mastercard. When I left the hospital the next day the cashier presented me the bill which was about 20000 of which you had charged the insurance company directl&nbsp;about 15000. The cashier showed me the receipt and told me that you are going to charge my MC for about 5000 for the accommodation and some beverages. Now it seems that you have charged my credit card for the whole sum of 40000 pesos. I want this corrected immediatelly and I&#39;m not going to approve the credit card bill. If you fail to refund my account I will let the credit card company take responsibility of any necessary legal actions because this is a serious fraud.</p><p>Panu Kuoppala</p>', '01/28/2015 04:58:40 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
