(323, 'Charity Rojo', '09307494680', 'rojocharity_0906@yahoo.com', 'Bacolod City', 'PH', 'info', 'Inquiries about Radiation ', '<p>Good Pm. Im Cha, we&#39;re from Bacolod City. The Doctor of my father in Iloilo City advises us to go there for a radiation for 30days because there&#39;s no radiation services in Bacolod nor in Iloilo. My ni refer sya na Dr. sa papa ko. We are not rich so we are worried if magkano ung Radiation? I heard about Plan .. Wala talaga kaming idea. My father has a .2 cm tumor in his larynx. Walang node. Sabi ng Dr. 98% daw gagaling ung Fr. ko.&nbsp; So it would be helpful to us if you can reply me as soon as possible so that we can prepare or you can give us an estimated figure. Thank you so much and God bless.</p>', '02/09/2015 05:00:07 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
