(337, 'Mendoza Rhea Dimapanis', '0639289089737', 'rheaguimba@gmail.com', 'Guimba / Nueva Ecija', 'PH', 'info', 'Chronical Sinusitis / cost estimate for a surgery', '<p>To whom it may concern</p><p>My life partner Miss Rhea Mendoza has a problem with here Nose. We went for a medical appraisal to the Bumrungrad International Hospital in Bangkok on November 2014. A Chronical Sinusitis was diagnosed at that time (medical report is available). It was agreed that Rhea should get a conventional therapy (antibiotics) first. A surgery was discussed for later; if no improvement should occur. After 3 months it is clear that a surgery is inevitable.</p><p>I would like to know how to proceed if Rhea decides to get the surgery at the Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital. In particular, I should have an offer for the estimated cost before making an appointment. Would a surgery be possible in March/April 2015? Rhea Mendoza lives in the Philippines and it would be convenient for her to travel to Cebu.</p><p>Thank you and best regards<br />Beni Kaspar</p><p>Would you please address your reply to me?</p><p>Beni Kaspar<br />Rosenweg 16e<br />CH-8413 Neftenbach<br />Switzerland<br />+41796006868<br /><a href=\"mailto:beni.kaspar@outlook.com\">beni.kaspar@outlook.com</a></p>', '02/15/2015 05:08:05 pm', 'unread', 'Archive'),
(338, 'Dr Catherine Bacus', '61402532686', 'cathbacus@gmail.com', 'Melbourne', 'AU', 'Admin', 'URGENT ATTENTION: CXR report for Jubylyn Erebias DOB 9 Jun 1985', '<p>This is a message for the RADIOLOGY DEPARTMENT</p><p>Maayong Buntag,</p><p>My name is Dr Catherine Bacus from Melbourne Australia. I am awaiting the arrival of my sister in law in Melbourne - she is due to fly out from Cebu TODAY MONDAY 16TH FEBRUARY. &nbsp;However, she is still awaiting the report for her CXR that was performed on Wed 11th February.&nbsp;</p><p>Could I please request that you report this as soon as possible this morning and forward the completed report to the requesting clinic/e-Medical/Immigration department so that the visa can be processed?</p><p>Salamat</p><p>Dr Catherine Bacus</p>', '02/15/2015 07:15:23 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
