(343, 'Charissa Hortelano', '09325808161', 'youraccess@ymail.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'delivery', 'Delivery Charges/non package maternity', '<p>Hi,</p><p>I&#39;m due this April probably 2nd week of April 2015. I haven&#39;t avail any maternity packages with any hospitals. I&#39;m still looking which hospitals would be best deal for my delivery. Would be kind to give atleast estimation of the charges for normal and CS delivery?</p><p>Thanks,</p><p>Charissa Hortelano</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '02/17/2015 01:32:35 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
(344, 'Christine Joy Mutia', '09081830261', 'mutiachristinejoy@yahoo.com', 'Misamis Occidental', 'PH', 'info', 'To get medical exams for immigration applicants', '<p><strong>Dear maa&#39;m/sir,</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;How can I get phone numbers from the good office of Dr. Maureen and Dr. Alberto Santos for our medical exams as applicants in the immigration? So that I can book my appointment to Dr.Maureen Santos or Dr.Alberto Santos as soon as possible.This is to inquire what are the exact phone numbers so that I can call them.I can&#39;t contact their previous numbers...I hope this would help as soon you read message.Thank you.</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Have a good day ahead!</strong></p>', '02/17/2015 04:27:27 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
