(349, 'Florelie Lascuna', '639273250174', 'flolascuna@gmail.com', 'Cebu', 'PH', 'info', 'Inquiry - Center for Cancer', '<p>Hi I would like to inquire how much ordinary chemotherapy costs?&nbsp;</p><p>My mother has undergone mastectomy and has been advised to undergo Chemotherapy. She was advised by the Surgical oncologist to undergo Ordinary Chemotherapy for 6 months.</p><p>If you could refer us to a Medical Oncologist for the prescription? and also if you can send us a ballpark of your chemotherapy pricing.<br /><br />We hope to here from you soon. As she need to do it by end of February.</p>', '02/17/2015 09:18:58 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
