(354, 'Adriel Dave A. Alvarez', '09222245901', 'parakletoshelp@gmail.com', 'San Francisco Cebu, (Camotes Islands)', 'PH', 'info', 'Inquiry on securing copies of lab tests .', '<p>Good day CDUH Management and Staff.</p><p>I am a recent patient at CDUH , confined last Feb. 12 to 14, 2015 under the medical care of Dr. Leah Villamor for &nbsp;my&nbsp;hypertension urgency case.</p><p>In this regard, may I request for a copy/copies of the lab tests i underwent within my confinement period? &nbsp;These include:&nbsp;</p><p>1. &nbsp;2d echo&nbsp;</p><p>2. &nbsp;Blood tests</p><p>3. Chest xray</p><p>Would it be possible to send them to me via email as I am currently residing in the town of San Francisco in Camotes islands, Cebu.</p><p>Many thanks for your kind reply which I hope would be favorable.</p><p>Best,</p><p>Adriel Dave A. Alvarez</p><p>email: parakletoshelp@gmail.com, alvarez_ad@yahoo.com</p><p>mob ph: 0922-224-5901</p>', '02/19/2015 09:06:21 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
(355, 'Joel Virador', '639396265552', 'jmvirador@gmail.com', 'Quezon City', 'PH', 'info', 'Looking for Medical Record MRI', 'Hello Cebu Doctors,<br />\n<br />\nI Would like to request a copy of my MRI of my cervical spine c1 c2 was 2002-2003 (OUT Patient )i am going to undergo operation here in manila as soon as possible  the doctor needs the MRI film to see the condition of my spine before i was undergo operation i hope you can accommodate my concerned i hoping for you reply in my email <br />\n<br />\nThank you very much<br />\nJoel M Virador ', '02/20/2015 01:59:43 pm', 'read', 'Archive'),
