(364, 'Manuel Noval', '0917-543-9912', 'manny.n@rnmdynamics.com', 'Lapulapu City', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Waste Water Treatment', '<p>Dear Sir/Madame,</p><p>Our company, RNM Dynamics Phils. Inc. has one of it`s product which may be of interest to your company. We employ an Advance Oxidation Process waste water treatment system which is the most cost effective system nowadays. We have installed our AOP system here in Cebu at Gaisano Capital sites, Mendero Hospital in Consolacion and many hospitals in Luzon. I wish to present our product to your management and further elaborate on the benefits of the AOP system. Please contact me at my contact numbers or email address as shown. Thank you for your time and hoping to serve you soon.</p><p>Manny Noval</p><p>Cebu Branch Manager</p><p>RNM Dynamics Phils. Inc.</p>', '02/24/2015 01:15:29 pm', 'read', 'Archive');
