(365, 'Marie Engler', '004917632829354', 'maengler@students.uni-mainz.de', 'Mainz', 'DE', 'info', 'clinical clerkship', '<p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><br />\n <w:WordDocument><br />\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View><br />\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom><br />\n  <w:TrackMoves/><br />\n  <w:TrackFormatting/><br />\n  <w:HyphenationZone>21</w:HyphenationZone><br />\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/><br />\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/><br />\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid><br />\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent><br />\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText><br />\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/><br />\n  <w:LidThemeOther>DE</w:LidThemeOther><br />\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian><br />\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript><br />\n  <w:Compatibility><br />\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/><br />\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/><br />\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/><br />\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/><br />\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/><br />\n   <w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/><br />\n   <w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/><br />\n   <w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/><br />\n   <w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/><br />\n   <w:Word11KerningPairs/><br />\n   <w:CachedColBalance/><br />\n  </w:Compatibility><br />\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel><br />\n  <m:mathPr><br />\n   <m:mathFont m:val=\"Cambria Math\"/><br />\n   <m:brkBin m:val=\"before\"/><br />\n   <m:brkBinSub m:val=\"&#45;-\"/><br />\n   <m:smallFrac m:val=\"off\"/><br />\n   <m:dispDef/><br />\n   <m:lMargin m:val=\"0\"/><br />\n   <m:rMargin m:val=\"0\"/><br />\n   <m:defJc m:val=\"centerGroup\"/><br />\n   <m:wrapIndent m:val=\"1440\"/><br />\n   <m:intLim m:val=\"subSup\"/><br />\n   <m:naryLim m:val=\"undOvr\"/><br />\n  </m:mathPr></w:WordDocument><br />\n</xml><![endif]--></p><p>Dear Doctors of Cebu Doctors University Hospital,</p><p>with this correspondence we apply for a clinical clerkship of 30 days in your hospital in September 2015.</p><p>We are two female students of Human Medicine, University of Mainz, Germany. In summer 2015, we will be in the fifth year of our studies.<br />During our medical education, we have to do some electives in several clinical departments. We have already done some internships in neurology, radiology, gynecology and general and pediatric medicine.</p><p>For the time being, we both also work on our dissertation theses in internal medicine and endocrinology.</p><p>Being in the clinical phase of our medical studies, we are open-minded to see how daily medicine works in a renowned Filipino Hospital and are very interested in working in various medical departments. The contact to local physicians, students and patients motivates us to spend our medical clerkship at Cebu Doctors University Hospital.</p><p>As we would like to get experience in any medical disciplines, we are interested in any possible clinical specialisation, especially in internal medicine and gynecology. It would be great, if there will be a possibility to get to know your culture and the health care system from a practical point of view.</p><p><br />Of course we are able to hand in later other certificates such as our CVs, a letter of recommendation, vaccination cards or certificates of conduct.</p><p>Thank you very much for your notice and the first contact,<br />Best regards,</p><p>&nbsp;Elisa Christina M&uuml;ller&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Marie Carolin Engler</p><p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><br />\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" DefUnhideWhenUsed=\"true\"<br />\n  DefSemiHidden=\"true\" DefQFormat=\"false\" DefPriority=\"99\"<br />\n  LatentStyleCount=\"267\"><br />\n  <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"0\" SemiHidden=\"false\"<br />\n   UnhideWhenUsed=\"false\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"Normal\"/><br />\n  <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"9\" SemiHidden=\"false\"<br />\n   UnhideWhenUsed=