(394, 'Paula Denise Endaya', '027227722', 'pde_endaya@focusmedia.com.ph', 'Pasig City', 'PH', 'marketing', 'Business Proposal from FocusMedia Audiovisuals Inc.', '<p>To whom it may concern,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Good day!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I am Paula Denise Endaya from FocusMedia Audiovisuals Inc., we are a digital out-of-home advertising agency based in Manila. We are in the process of expanding our business in Visayas and in Mindanao. In connection with this, Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital&nbsp;is one of the locations that we desire to be a part of our expansion project. We would like to offer you a business proposal about installation of LCD screens in your hospital&rsquo;s lobby/waiting area, all expenses paid by FocusMedia. You may use those LCD screens for your announcements, hospital directory, or ads.</p><p>Should you want to know more about the business plan, our team will be visiting Cebu City on March 23-25 for ocular visits and we would like to come over to your office to present the proposal in full details at your most convenient time within March 23 &ndash; March 25, 2015. We would be very grateful for a few minutes of your time.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Hoping for your response.</p><p>Thank you very much!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sincerely yours,</p><p>Paula Denise Endaya</p><p>Multimedia Artist</p><p>FocusMedia Audiovisuals Inc.</p>', '03/12/2015 11:42:07 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
