(401, 'Melanie', '09069378825', 'cloud_sykesg45@yahoo.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Application form', '<p>Melanie S. Alturas</p><p>F. Calderon St. Cebu City</p><p>Contact No. 09069378825</p><p>cloud_sykesg45@yahoo.com</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Manager,</p><p>Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital<br />Osme&ntilde;a Blvd, Cebu City, Cebu 6000</p><p>March 15, 2015</p><p>Dear Sir/ Madam;</p><p>I am writing to explore the posibility of employment in your reputable firm. I am genuinely interested to work in your prestigous company as Office Clerk that suit to my course. I am a BS Computer Science graduate at Bohol Island State University, Balilihan Bohol. I was very excited to know about your job vacancy.</p><p>Please get in touch with me at your earliest convenience at 09069378825 to discuss the parameters of Office clerk position.<br /><br />Thank you for your time!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sincerely yours,</p><p>MELANIE S. ALTURAS</p>', '03/15/2015 10:12:05 am', 'read', 'Archive'),
