(404, 'John Branson', '6391662337497', 'john.branson@shawneemission.org', 'Shawnee Mission, Kansas', 'US', 'Admin', 'Visiting Cebu', '<p>Dear Administrator,</p><p>I am a Healthcare Administrator in the United States with an interest in International Healthcare and International Public Health. I am planning on visiting Cebu in 2015 with dates to be determined.</p><p>I am aware of the reputation of Cebu Doctors&rsquo; University Hospital so I would very much like to tour your hospital when I visit. Any time I can spend with healthcare leaders while on vacation would be a real treat for me.</p><p>Would there be anyone at Cebu Doctor&rsquo;s University Hospital interested in exchanging ideas sometime?</p><p>Thank you,</p><p>John Branson</p><p>P.S.&nbsp; That is not my phone number, but rather a friend there in the Philippines. It was a required field for this form.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '03/19/2015 02:21:14 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
