(557, 'Brian Jones', '00353873805443', '777brianjones@gmail.com', 'Kildare', 'IE', 'info', 'Is there a hand/plastic  surgeon who corrects Dupuytrens Contracture', '<p><strong>I have recurrent dupuytrens contracture on two fingers of my left hand(two operations so far). Due to involvement of scar tissue I have been told that the most suitable procedure now would be dermo-fasciectomy (operation with skin graft).</strong></p><p><strong>1. Price for normal fasciectomy (as preformed twice already), including breakdown of costs.</strong></p><p><strong>2. Price for dermofasciectomy (if considered necessary), including breakdown of costs</strong></p><p><strong>3. Does the surgeon speak good English?</strong></p><p><strong>4. Can I speak to someone in English on the phone?</strong></p>', '06/02/2015 01:12:59 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
