(912, 'Tabea Clara Schubert', '004917634496903', 'tab.s@gmx.de', 'Kiel', 'DE', 'info', 'clinical elective for 2 months', '<p>Dear Ladies and Gentlemen,</p><p>we are 4 medical students at the Christian-Albrechts-University of Kiel in Germany and momentarily in the 5th year of our studies. In May 2016 we will very likely have passed our 2nd state examination and will be ready to start into the Practical Year (last year of education) which we have to absolve during our course of studies in Germany.</p><p>As we are very interested in the subject of surgery we want to apply for a 2-month clinical training in Cebu starting in September 2016. (05.09.16-30.10.16)</p><p>We would be happy to absolve this training in your hospital as we are really interested in getting to know a foreign health system and the daily routine in a hospital abroad.</p><p>If you would write us an email (tab.s@gmx.de), we could send you further information like for example our CVs and a Dean letter.</p><p>Yours sincerely,</p><p>Laura Gottschalk, Yu-Ri Shin, Elisa Schroeder and Tabea Schubert</p>', '11/11/2015 05:05:46 am', 'unread', 'Pending'),
