(962, 'PATRICK BENJ S BERNABE', '09177751069', 'patrickbenjbernabe@yahoo.com', 'Lapu Lapu', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Proposal letter', '<p><strong>Dear Sir/Madame,</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Good day! We would like to take this opportunity to introduce our company <strong>Global Steps Academy Inc.</strong>, An English as secondary Language School located in Mactan Island. We cater complete ESL education to Japanese whose main goal is to learn English on their convenient way. Majority of our students are Japanese nurses, they study medical English and we believe that one way to mold their skills is to observe how Filipino nurses provide a great quality of care to their patients.</p><p>Your School&nbsp;is well known for calibrated high competency level of practice when it comes to medical field. We believe that such service that you provide to your trainees have a very good potential to be well known globally. It is in this respect that we would like to extend our interest in forming a partnership with your institution. We heard that your institution caters medical &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;tourism or affiliation system, we believe that our service could well compliment to your great service.</p><p>At your respect I could send you our company&rsquo;s introductory profile for your perusal, or you may peruse our website should you be interested in this cooperation or have questions in this regards, please do not hesitate to give me a feedback you could reach me through this email <a href=\"mailto:patrickbenjbernabe@yahoo.com\">patrickbenjbernabe@yahoo.com</a> .</p><p>Thank you very much, and we hope to receive your favorably response.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sincerely yours,</p><p><strong>Patrick Benj Bernabe, RN</strong></p><p><strong>Team Leader </strong></p><p><strong>Global Steps Academy Grace International</strong></p><p><strong>0917-775-1069 &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '12/14/2015 02:20:57 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
