(1006, 'Daniel Keller', '392-0343', 'dkeller@cis.edu.ph', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'hr', 'Cebu International School - Job Shadowing Request', '<p>Good Afternoon,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My name is Daniel Keller and I am a teacher at Cebu International School (CIS). Here at CIS, myself and two other colleagues are working to create real world experiences for our students. As part of this effort we are reaching out to the most influential community business leaders and partners to facilitate job shadowing experiences. These meaningful real world engagements can help to foster lifelong relationships between Cebu Doctor&#39;s University Hospital and the future leaders of Cebu.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our school has set aside four consecutive days, beginning&nbsp;<strong>Tuesday</strong><strong>,&nbsp;</strong><strong>February 2nd through Friday, February 5th,&nbsp;</strong>in order to allow students to&nbsp;take part in this opportunity. The goal is to have 3-4 students, accompanied by a teacher, shadow various professionals in your hospital. For example students could spend a day interacting with doctors, nurses, technicians accounts management, insurance claims, or other areas that you deem to be beneficial. Each day the students could rotate between the positions so that they may be able experience multiple aspects of the hospital&#39;s daily operations.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We are reaching out to you in hopes of establishing a mutually beneficial partnership for not only this year, but also for those to come. I hope to speak with you this week so that my colleagues and I may have ample time to make the&nbsp;proper&nbsp;arrangements. Please contact me at&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:dkeller@cis.edu.ph\">dkeller@cis.edu.ph</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;0906-392-0343.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Respectfully,&nbsp;</p><p>Daniel Keller</p>', '01/07/2016 04:25:58 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
