(1014, 'Tommy Zhou', '0031652076823', 'x.y.t.zhou@student.rug.nl', 'Groningen', 'NL', 'Admin', 'Internship Public Health', '<p>Dear Sir/madam,</p><p>At the end of October 2016, I will have my Public Health internship. I am planning to do the internship in the Philippines. However, our university does not have connections in the country. Therefore, it is my task to find a place where they can offer me an internship.&nbsp;<br /><br />Currently, I am in my 2nd year of the Master&#39;s Degree of Science in Medicine at the University of Groningen, in the Netherlands. The internship I am looking for should be about Public Health. What our University require is an internship supervised by a certified doctor.</p><p>Is there a possibility to join your programs/missions in the field of Public Health? Or do you maybe know other organizations where I can apply for an internship in this field? The internship will take approximately eight weeks.&nbsp;<br /><br />I hope to hear from you.&nbsp;</p><p>Kind regards,</p><p>Tommy Zhou</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/11/2016 02:08:06 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
