(1069, 'Anna Grace Cadampog', '63324213250', 'graceydan_25@yahoo.com', 'Dubai', 'AE', 'info', 'Guarantee of payment under Insurance', '<p>Hello,</p><p>Good day!</p><p>I&#39;d like to inquire if the hospital accepts Guarantee of Payment&nbsp;from an Insurance Company.</p><p>I am currently working here in Dubai United Arab Emirates and i got my Nextcare Insurance. I am pregnant and planning to give birth in my home place in Cebu. I am inquiring in advance about how can i avail with my insurance direct billing if Cebu Doctor&#39;s University Hospital particularly North General Hospital which is close to my house accepts such policy.</p><p>I will be visiting the hospital personally too before i will be due for my delivery on August 25 as EDD when i will arrive in Cebu to ask about the procedure and will have my doctor&#39;s visit/s for check in your hospital too.</p><p>Please advise if its possible to have a direct billing c/o my Nextcare Insurance. I will be asking for a price quotation for&nbsp;your delivery charges prior from my EDD so that i can send such qoutation to Nextcare for payment preparation. Your accounting department and Nextcare will communicate thus before i will be admitted for delivery everything will be finalized&nbsp;and before&nbsp;i will be discharged check payment will be deposited by Nextcare. The same thing they do with&nbsp;my other colleagues in other Philippine Hospitals.</p><p>Please advise.</p><p>Thank you.</p><p>Regards,</p><p>Anna Grace Phua Cadampog</p>', '02/09/2016 08:52:41 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
