cting a research study on the Service Quality of Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital&nbsp;here in Cebu City.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>In lieu with this we would like to ask for your permission to conduct an interview with the management representative and to conduct a survey to your customers. Rest assured that all data gathered will be treated with utmost confidentiality and for academic purpose only.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Should you have any inquiries regarding our study you may contact us at any time through this number: Pimentel, Nikki 09223676600 or Nudalo, Jhyke 09420727081</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We are hoping for your positive response.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Respectfully yours,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Nikki Rafael C. Pimentel</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Endorsed by:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Dr. Roberto H. Visitacion</p><p>Research Advisor</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><!--EndFragment--></p>', '02/10/2016 09:13:43 am', 'read', 'Done'),
(1071, 'Judith Digal', '639183673821', 'cjtimbal@yahoo.com', 'TAGBILARAN CITY', 'PH', 'info', 'Mammography', '<p>Good Day! My sister&#39;s obgyne recommended her for&nbsp;a mammogram&nbsp;in your hospital. Since we are from Bohol, may I ask if we can still be accommodated when we arrived in your hospital past 9am already, since we&#39;re planning to take fast craft which would leave here the earliest 6:05am.&nbsp;I hope to hear from you. Thank you in advance.</p>', '02/10/2016 11:31:25 am', 'unread', 'Pending'),
