(1073, 'Marrie Chris Cuison', '09430625948', 'marriecuison@gmail.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'marketing', 'Billboard proposal from Pacific Mall Mandaue', '<p>Good Day Madam/ Sir,<br /><br />Pacific Mall Mandaue is located in M.C Briones Corner UN Ave, Estancia, Mandaue City, 6014 Cebu, Philippines and has been operating designing marketing campaigns for over a decade. I have a billboard proposal for you.<br />We are pleased you chose to call us.<br /><br />We have put together hundreds of successful campaigns for businesses like yours. We specialize in helping small and medium-sized businesses create innovative campaigns that include direct marketing and billboard design.</p><p><br />Should you choose to sign a contract with &nbsp;we can immediately begin the creative side of the campaign,&nbsp;We are open to your suggestions and counter proposals which you may think beneficial for both of us. Should you have inquiries, you may reach us at tel. no.&nbsp;<strong>(032) 239-7956</strong>&nbsp;or at&nbsp;<strong>09236226541</strong>&nbsp;or email us at&nbsp;<strong><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:dbracero08@gmail.com\">dbracero08@gmail.com</a></strong></p><p>Thank you very much and looking forward to your favorable reply.</p>', '02/10/2016 03:35:47 pm', 'unread', 'Pending'),
(1074, 'Kyle daniel T. Lajot', '09157691094', 'Kylelajot@ymail.com', 'Cebu city', 'PH', 'info', 'Contact number; office/clinic for scheduling', '<p>Hi, I&#39;m a patient of Dr. Roselllo and I was hoping your department would provide me with the contact number of his clinic since I can&#39;t personally go at this moment, I&#39;m also a student of Cebu Doctors&#39; University. You may contact me through my personal number or via e-mail.&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you and God bless.</p>', '02/10/2016 04:47:49 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
