(1084, 'Daniel Wright', '640223235508', 'dan@findcancertreatments.org', 'New Zealand', 'NZ', 'marketing', 'Cancer Treatments Required', '<p>Hi There,</p><p>I am the content curator for &ldquo;Find Cancer Treatments&ldquo; (findcancertreatments.org), a New and Free online cancer database service that provides the latest information on cancer treatments, facilities, hospitals, services, clinics, organizations and foundations from all around the world.</p><p>We have come across your website http://cduh.com.ph/services/centers/cancer and believe it would be of value to our audience. We would like to include it in our cancer treatments directory free of charge. We would like to ask for your permission to create a draft listing for you. From this you will get your own login details which gives you full control of what information is shown on your listing. You can update, edit or delete anything at any time.</p><p>Our Aim: We understand that when someone is diagnosed with cancer they are often left feeling alone, overwhelmed and are often unaware of the full range of services that are available to them globally. Our objective is to equip both the patients (as well as the friends and family) with the full range of cancer treatments available today in a modern and easy to use online database. This will help them avoid the added stress of late nights researching online.</p><p>Please respond within 48hrs if you would like to be included in the directory, we would love to include you, and I am sure our members will benefit from your information.</p><p>Regards,</p><p>Daniel Wright</p>', '02/12/2016 10:13:47 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
