(1218, 'Daniel Sebastian Majorski', '004915254126106', 'd.majorski@outlook.com', 'Cologne', 'DE', 'hr', 'Doctors Practice ', '<p>Hello dear Sir, dear Madam,</p><p>my name is Daniel S. Majorski from Cologne, Germany, currently in my last year of University, studying Medicine. After I visited the Philippines last month, I decided to come back to the Philippines and the Cebu area in particular and wanted to combine it with a doctors practice. In my country, after completing all theoretical courses, we are obliged to collect one year of practical experience in hospitals. This so called PJ(practical year), is divided into three parts. One medical, one surgical and one field of choice. I am interested in fulfilling 2-4 months, depending on your capacity, of my surgical trimester at your University hospital. Please let me know whether you can provide me with a possibilty as such. If you as a hospital, are interested in letting me fulfill my doctors practice at your facility I will get in touch with my home university and contact your afterwards. Herefore please provide me with an email adress of the Universities colleague for In-Going international students or someone I can contact on this matter.</p><p>Thank you very much in advance,</p><p>Kind Regards, Daniel Majorski</p>', '04/18/2016 09:23:15 pm', 'unread', 'Pending'),
