(1238, 'Sung Soo Jo', '09065010410', 'ssj10012000@naver.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'Admin', 'I\'m totally disappoited!', '<p>I went Cebu doc on 18th becoz I had a terrible headache and stomachache. And I was hospitalized at that time room 417. Nextday doctor said &quot;you can go home&quot; so&nbsp;I was waiting&nbsp;next&nbsp;sign&nbsp;but&nbsp;nurse&nbsp;came&nbsp;only to check&nbsp;vital sign.&nbsp;So&nbsp;I&nbsp;just thought&nbsp;like&nbsp;I&nbsp;can go home&nbsp;tomorrow&nbsp;coz&nbsp;I&nbsp;was still&nbsp;painful.&nbsp;And&nbsp;nextday&nbsp;20th,&nbsp;doctor&nbsp;also said&nbsp;you can go&nbsp;home&nbsp;before lunch.&nbsp;So&nbsp;I expected to go home&nbsp;but&nbsp;at that time&nbsp;also&nbsp;nurse just checked&nbsp;vital sign&nbsp;only and I asked evening Can I go home now? and nurse said &quot;not now I should contact doctor&quot;so I said &quot;Then can I go early in the tomorrow morning? coz I dont want to pay tomorrow&#39;s room fee&quot; like that.&nbsp;Finally nextday&nbsp;21th&nbsp;In the morning 9am. nurse came to room so I asked again I want to check out. But at that time also nurse said I will inform you soon. And I waited until 11am. And man nurse came to room so I asked one more time! like I dont want to stay more than 12pm coz after12 room fee will be charged one more day.&nbsp;And he said ok I will check and inform you. And waited again.............! At 4pm. finally I could get list of medicine and bill. And I found out day21&#39;s room fee also charged so I complaint to nurse and waited 2hours again and he said I cannot contact with morning time nurse but you can stay until tomorrow when morning nurse come or go home with leave your contact number. So I just said I want to go home now! becoz I dont want to absent my job even one more day. And I came back to home. And as I known he still doesnt contact!! Why? Is 2500peso so small to me becoz of Im a Korean? Im really mad and I dont know where should I contact to solve this. Should I upload on face