(1262, 'Kristil Evan Patulin', '0221253438', 'patz_2306@yahoo.com', 'Alexandra', 'NZ', 'Admin', 'Claim refund inquiry', 'Dear Sir/ Madam,<br />\n<br />\nI had contacted the Philhealth Corporate Action Centre about the status of my refund and they gathered the information from the Benefits Administration Section stated below:<br />\n<br />\n\"Per our records, the claim is still pending, awaiting the hospital of confinement\'s re-submission of the claim documents, together with the Waiver Form for Directly Filed Claims.<br />\nAs such, you may coordinate with the hospital of confinement and update the status of your claim documents.\"<br />\n<br />\nI would like to get some clarifications and suggestions of what are those important documents to be presented when I get there to claim the refund? Would it be too long to process it? I just hope not coz my time in Cebu is very short only..<br />\nThank you. Looking forward to hearing it from you. <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n', '05/06/2016 06:20:23 pm', 'read', 'Done');
