(1422, 'Heinz-Gerd Loedige', '09208807838', 'loedige@email.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Dr. Mejarito, my cystoscopy on Aug. 2nd', '<p>Dear Dr. Mejarito,</p><p>On our 4-week Thailand trip I discovered fresh blood in my urine a few days ago. Today I had a cystoscopy.<br />The tumor has reappeared at two spots and two yellow-white urinal stones have grown exactly there and are clearly to be seen. I have been advised to have another TUR and then BCG.</p><p>Health insurance cover for all this I only have in Germany - that means I have to go back &#39;home&#39; although I do not live there anymore. I a few days I will get my retirement visa for the Philippines where I wanted to live for the rest of my life...<br /><br />Kind Regards<br />Freundliche Gruesse<br />Gerd Loedige</p>', '07/13/2016 11:00:37 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
