(1428, 'Fabio Munzinger', '0041765310914', 'Fabio.munzinger@students.unibe.ch', 'Zurich', 'CH', 'hr', 'medical elective 2017', '<p>Dear Sir or Madam</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I am a student at the Medical Faculty of the University of Bern, Switzerland. My final year is divided in different elective periods, in which I would like to spend one month (June 2017) abroad. I found your address via internet and your hospital seemed very interesting for collecting new medical experiences.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>In case your hospital offers internships for foreign students, I would like to apply for a clinical clerkship in your hospital from 29th May 2017 to 23th June 2017. I would be particularly interested in getting an insight in all fields of pediatric medicine.</p><p>Would it be possible for me to work in a clinical situation under the supervision of a MD?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>By the time I would like to come to your hospital, my curriculum will have been as follows:</p><p>- 2 years of preclinical studies</p><p>- 3 years of clinical studies including practical teaching programs in clinical clerkship of variable duration</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I would be most grateful if you could let me know as soon as possible whether you would consider me for a medical elective in the above mentioned period.</p><p>As I could not found many informations about an elective stay in the Philippines, it would also be helpful if you could send me further informations about your elective program and costs for a four week stay.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you in advance for your kind consideration.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Yours sincerely,</p><p>Fabio Munzinger</p>', '07/17/2016 12:09:25 am', 'read', 'Done'),
