(1438, 'Szilard Dulai', '1-226-500-2401', 'dulaisz@yahoo.ca', 'Guelph', 'CA', 'info', 'Inquiry for treatment ', '<p>Dear Lady /Gentleman !</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My name is Szilard Dulai&nbsp;from Guelph Ontario.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I would like to treat myself with a Hungarian serum ( CHOLESTEROL IMMUNIZATION ) which I bought in Hungary.&nbsp;</p><p>If You would be willing to do the blood work to me,&nbsp; I will get You at least two more patients for same treatments.&nbsp;</p><p>I hope it would be a lot of people who would be interested of decreasing the high cholesterol level!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sincerely</p><p>Szilard Dulai</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>tel:1.226.500.2401</p><p>201 Silvercreek PWY N. Unit 25</p><p>Guelph, ON, Canada</p><p>N1H 3T4</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Immunisation procedure with the CH Ag Preparation of the serum.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A./Preparation of the serum</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>1. Take about 10 ml of sterile native blood from the subject to be immunised.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Wait till the coagulation of the blood.&nbsp;</p><p>3. Make centrifugation with 3000 g During the 10 minutes</p><p>4. Divide the sterilised serum into nine equal parts into 2 ml syringes.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If You need more information:</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.ilchungary.com/treatments/cholesterol-immunization/\">http://www.ilchungary.com/treatments/cholesterol-immunization/</a></p>', '07/21/2016 06:35:26 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
