(1559, 'Albert Cabalda', '09399344010', 'Albertcabalda@icloud.com', 'Lapu-lapu City', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Terrible customer service at Mactan Doctors Hospital', '<p>Hi,<br /><br />Im writing this feedback to help your services be improved in the field of customer service.<br /><br />Last Sept 5.2016 around&nbsp;<a href=\"x-apple-data-detectors://0\">10.30pm</a>&nbsp;we decided with my parents to go to your facility since I have high regard to the expertise compared to our other neighbor hospital.<br />A PGI assisted me and have my stomach checked and I told him that my pain is 9 rating as 10 highest and I clearly inform him to be admitted. He asked instead of my insurance card since they will call and ask for approval. I requested him to stay inside the vicinity of the ER since the hallway is having a foul smell. Surprisingly, he replied &quot;di gyud sir, sa gawas gyud mo dapat maghulat (referring to the hallway where there was a long bench with a tv). So we did wait for 15 minutes and told us that we need to have the card swiped for outpatient lab test. We obeyed and followed their instructions and since the pain is totally unbearable, I hurriedly went to the comfort room to vomit. I asked my mom to have some sample to show to them and to be admitted.&nbsp;<br />As we tried to look for the PGI to show to him the sample, I decided to take a seat since the pain is still there. We saw another doctor, a lady doctor, and I asked her that i cant tolerate the pain . She was half meter away and I asked her to come closer as my tone was already on its peak . She was furious and got made and explained that there is a process. She then took my blood pressure. I explained to her that even the basic taking of stats were not performed when in fact the staff were the ones making the room crowded.<br />She then said that her patience rarely got consumed until she saw me. I explained to her that her staff was not listening to me instead they were pre occupied on the approval of my admission to my insurance company. She then starting saying that she was not the doctor who assisted me and U should not be shouting at her. I replied to her that she was not approaching closer earlier and she was saying &quot;what&quot; as a sign that cant hear me. Then she became silent..<br />She then asked her staff to accompany me to a bed for her to examine. I can see her lips trembling and she was examining the corners of my abdomen and her pressure contains anger. I apologize but she kept still her ego.<br /><a href=\"x-apple-data-detectors://1\">3am</a>&nbsp;when we got our room..<br /><br />Good thing the nurses on the 3rd floor were exceptional..<br /><br />Hope immediate actions should be taken since I will never recommend this hospital if the services were not friendly.<br /><br /><br />Respectfully yours,<br /><br />Albert</p>', '09/08/2016 01:41:19 pm', 'read', 'Done');
