(1597, 'Jonathan Shearer', '1234567890', 'jwsinchin@gmail.com', 'Beijing', 'CN', 'info', 'Gastroenterologist', '<p>In January, I had a standard checkup at Makati Medical Center, including gastrointestinal screening. The resultsshowed nothing to be concerned about.</p><p>However, there is&nbsp;<em>certainly</em>&nbsp;something to be concerned about and this is the second general checkup I have taken in the previous three or four years, both of which have showed nothing, despite my obvious symptoms.</p><p>I have had chronic diarrhea, gas, or constipation, or a combination of all three, off and on for around four years. Two or three times a year, there is some bleeding.</p><p>It is pretty clear to me that I need to see a gastroenterologist. It is becoming clear that the situation may be rather more severe than I imagined. I do not think I have IBS or colitis, but I am zoologist, not a medical practitioner. I work with reptiles and could easily be suffering from acute salmonensis, but I feel there is more to it than that.</p><p>I will arrive in Cebu at 10 am on October 12, and will only be staying for a few days. I would like to see a gastroenterologist that afternoon or. if that is not possible, then October 13, please. I really do not need to see another GP.</p><p>Phone numbers are of no use to me whatsoever. I need to conduct all this business by email.</p><p>Thanks</p>', '09/22/2016 06:42:24 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
(1598, 'Terry Nickel', '19413132442', 'tenraiofthemountain@gmail.com', 'sarasota/florida', 'US', 'Admin', 'Bill payment', '<p>I have a friend who is/will be a patient there Nicky Caballero, she will be needing dialysis.</p><p>I am interested in helping her pay medical expenses not covered by Philhealth.</p><p>However, I would prefer to pay you directly.</p><p>Please let me know everything I would need to do to make this work. What paperwork would you need, or other information. &nbsp;What forms the patient might need to fill out that would allow me to know what was owed.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you</p><p>Terry Nickel</p>', '09/23/2016 12:09:04 am', 'read', 'Done'),
(1599, 'Fumio Hasue', '81-438-36-1071', 'hafu82@yahoo.co.jp', 'Kisarazu-shi, Chiba prefecture', 'JP', 'info', 'Inquiring about patient information (Patient No. 630442)', '<p>Dear Dr. Bimbo Tequillo</p><p>This letter concerns the result of the Microbiology<br />of Mr. MITO, SHOJI (Patient No.630442), which was performed onSeptember 2, 2016<br />at CEBU DOCTOR&rsquo;S UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL where you are working.<br />I am a spine surgeon at Kimitsu Chuo Hospital in Chiba, Japan, and a primary doctor of Mr. MITO,<br />SHOJI following him in Japan.According to the report, the specimen you took was nasopharyngeal swab.I&rsquo;d like to know which sample you took at that time.<br />Did you extract it from abscess (aspiration) or pharyngeal mucosa (surface<br />wiping liquid) ?<br />If you took the sample from surface of pharyngeal mucosa, I will make an additional examination to detect the fungus causing an pyogenic vertebral osteomyelitis at cervical.<br />I would appreciate it, if you can e-mail me in detail.<br /><br />Thank you very much for your help in advance.<br /><br />Sincerely yours,<br /><br />Fumio Hasue, MD,PhD.<br />**************************<br />Kimitsu Chuo Hospital<br />Dept. of Orthop.<br />TEL: +81-438-36-1071<br />FAX: +81-438-36-3867<br />e-mail: <a target=\"_self\" href=\"mailto:hafu82@yahoo.co.jp\">hafu82@yahoo.co.jp</a></p>', '09/23/2016 09:58:25 am', 'read', 'Done'),
(1600, 'Russell Haney', '6309234994691', 'purltrhythm@yahoo.com', 'Iloilo, Iloilo', 'PH', 'info', 'Stem Cell Treatment for CHF also Compounding Pharmacy', '<p>I am seacrching for a cardiologist that knows stem cells for the possible treatment of CHF and also may use more natural methods to treat it. Plus I have a prescriptiom for Standard Trimex 5 ml. Does your pharmacy do liquid compounding and can they fill that. Let me know if you accept Visa for payment, how much for interview with doctor if one is there that does what I seek. Also how much for the prescription for standard trimix, I know I will probably need a doctor to write one for me here since mine is from the USA. Please answer soon, Thank You.</p>', '09/23/2016 10:48:37 am', 'read', 'Done'),
