p;</p><p>Dear Sir or Madam&nbsp;;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; As students in third year at Lyon Sud University, we are four girls requiring to complete a pratictal internship with a duration of six weeks. This internship will allow us to use all the methods and techniques we have had the opportunity to learn through our academic program. It is within this framework that we are contacting you in order to submit our application.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your hospital, with its serious reputation, could greatly benefit us and allow us to continue our training in the best possible conditions. We are not starting from zero as, in addition to having received primarily theoretical training, we already have some experience thanks to numerous french internship in different services, such as urology, geriatrics, pulmonology&hellip;It could be an advantage for&nbsp; us to complete an internship at your compagny.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Being a part of your hospital would be a great satisfaction for us and it will allow us to gain professional experience, improve a foreign language and discover a new culture and way of practising. We are motivated to learn and curious to take part in the life of your hospital.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We hope that our application interests you. Please do not hesitate to contact us, in case you require any further information.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Yours sincerely</p><p><!--EndFragment--></p>', '12/21/2016 07:15:40 pm', 'unread', 'Pending');
