(1787, 'Malou Diaz', '09238622902', 'maloud211@gmail.com', 'Munster, Indiana', 'US', 'Admin', 'To:  Dr Consolacion Cutillar;   Re:  Lab results', '<p>I am a patient of Dr. Cutillar who I&#39;ve seen on Dec 19, 2016. &nbsp;I&#39;ve&nbsp;have tried to get in touch with her regarding the lab results she ordered, but unfortunately, either she is busy or the secretary is busy. On Tuesday or Wednesday, I dropped off a copy of the lab resutls at her office in Diaz Building.&nbsp;I&#39;m here in Cebu for a very short time and wanted so bad to talk to her about the results where the numbers are way off the normal limits. &nbsp;I&#39;m hoping this message could get to her somehow. &nbsp;Doctors should have other means of communicating to their patients especially when they are going on vacation for a number of days. &nbsp;I can&#39;t imagine if the test comes up with negative/critical figures, the patient is at a loss and may end up in a compromising situation. &nbsp;I may sound like ranting but Doctors have responsibilities to their patients. &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Malou Diaz</p>', '12/23/2016 12:38:31 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
(1788, 'David Selmser', '09276452337', 'pauldanielando@gmail.com', 'Dumaguete, Negros O', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Appointment with Dr Leah Villamor, Internal Medicine', '<p>Dr Susan Micaela Ozoa Denura has referred me: David Selmser, 73 yo male - narrowed &nbsp;Carotid Artery - need a Stent. Appointment late Dec?</p><p>I will be in Cebu on other matters Dec 30 to Jan 7. &nbsp;I could come earlier or stay longer if I can get an appointment to see Dr Leah Villamor with an intention to get a stent into my 80% restricted narrowed carotid artery.</p><p>Pls let me know on my email</p><p>David Selmser</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '12/23/2016 12:55:28 pm', 'unread', 'Pending'),
