(1820, 'Francesca Magcaleng', '639988506501', 'cesca@equalitymarketing.com', 'Cebu City', 'PH', 'marketing', 'Save the Children Exhibit Space', '<p>Good day,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This is Cheska Magcaleng, representing Save the Children Philippines. Save the Children is the world&rsquo;s leading NGO for children. We are currently conducting awareness campaigns regarding our programs to help save kids. Last 2016, we expanded our operations by putting up a campaign office in Cebu City. We are looking for more partners to support us in our campaign. With this said, we would like to express our intention to hold an exhibit in Cebu Doctors&#39; University Hospital. We would like to request for your assistance regarding securing an exhibit space. We hope you can accommodate us, as it would mean a huge support for our campaigns. If you have any questions regarding our exhibit, please do not hesitate to contact me. Thank you and looking forward to our partnership for Filipino children.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Regards,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Francesca Magcaleng</p><p>Events Officer</p><p>M: 639988506501 ; (02)4634448</p><p>E:&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:cesca@equalitymarketing.com\">cesca@equalitymarketing.com</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/06/2017 09:12:13 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
