(1919, 'Jeffelyn Marie Ines', '09394922264', 'jmines.04@gmail.com', 'Koronadal City', 'PH', 'info', 'Patient', 'Good day!<br />\nI would like to ask how to get an appointment for my niece, she has been diagnosed with B acute lymphocytic leukemia, with aberrant myeloid antigen expression.  If it would be possible that i will just bring all her lab test results and show them to Dr Jose Antonio Quivetis. Because im afraid  she would get ill going there. Hope to hear from you soon. Thank you and God bless.', '02/18/2017 12:02:56 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
(1920, 'Frank kahn', '09198220746', 'Fksybarite@cs.com', 'Cebu city', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Marylou ong is a QUACK', '<p>You should not have Marylou Ong as a practicing doctor. She does not know what she is doing and is stupid. I went for an examination to see if I had any skin cancer to worry about...she barely examined me, and she looked at the two spots of concerns on my back and she asked ME which spot she wanted me to ask her about, WHAT A TOTAL IDIOT, if she was a real doctor she wouldn&#39;t have asked &nbsp;me the stupidest question I have ever heard in my life, she would have looked at both and given me her opinion, not asked me my opinion. I am not the doctor, that&#39;s why I paid her...and then she didn&#39;t care enough to even look at the rest of my body....I&#39;ve been to many dermatologists, many caring dermatologists, she didn&#39;t care, I would call her a real C U N T, and I think heir English is good enough to understand this....you can forward this to her, and please respond and acknowledge you received this and you will take action to do something about this pathetic woman who calls herself a dermatologist.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '02/21/2017 08:25:07 am', 'read', 'Done'),
