(1923, 'Kaye Dumancas', '09175785896', 'mariekrisd@yahoo.com', 'Bacolod', 'PH', 'Admin', 'Wrong Diagnosis', '<p>i would like to call your attention with regards to wrong diagnosis. My family and I were having our weekend vacation in Cebu when my sister felt pain after urinating in the morning, but she said she&#39;ll just drink more water. But the pain didnt disappear and instead radiated to her lower back making it hard for her to walk without bending her. We decided to bring her to Cebu doctors Hospital. A resident doctor assessed her and we complied with the the CBC and Urine tests. After we got the results another male doctor came in. Stating that everything and all the results are normal, though he advised for ultrasound of KUB. We had our sister checked her in Riverside Hospital Bacolod and the doctor said that there was a presence of blood in the urine which your doctor did not specify.&nbsp;</p>', '02/21/2017 03:16:48 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
(1924, 'Michelle Obida', '09177266458', 'michellealivio44@gmail.com', 'Consolacion Cebu', 'PH', 'info', 'Ask for the schedule', '<p>Hello!</p><p>I just ask if Dr. Ma. Asuncion Tremedal is available or she is &nbsp;on her clinic on &nbsp;Saturday Febuary 25,2017.Thank you and God Bless.</p>', '02/21/2017 06:43:31 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
