(1932, 'Airah dajay', '09265140736', 'Cymelodz143@yahoo.com', 'Cebu city', 'PH', 'info', 'Pregnant or not? ', 'Hello. I hope you can help me. I am about 2 months late period today. When I had my first month late, I tested a home pregnancy test twice at the same day, same urine and same time. I got negative. After that I havent take pregnancy test again till now. I want to see a doctor but I cant afford to go for a check up. Until now I havent got my period. Please help. This is my first time being late at period in two months. ', '02/24/2017 11:50:25 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
