(2022, 'Dr Buenaventura C. Ramos, Jr.', '09176285021', 'billevemig@gmail.com', 'Cebu City ', 'PH', 'webmaster', 'Doctor\'s Information', '<p>Hi there!</p><p>I am Dr. Buenaventura Ramos, Jr., and I am a member of the CDUH Medical Staff. My name is in your website in the &quot;Our Doctors&quot; part but it lacks some information and some aren&#39;t accurate, like the phone number and clinic schedule. I&#39;d be glad and grateful if you can correct them and add items to the ones left blank.</p><p>Here&#39;s the complete and correct information: (I&#39;ll put in bold the ones that were missing or needs correction)</p><p>DR. BUENAVENTURA C. RAMOS,<strong> JR.</strong></p><p>Specialty: Internal Medicine</p><p>Subspecialty: Oncology</p><p><strong>Contact #:</strong> <strong>(+63 32) 255 2408</strong></p><p><strong>Room/Clinic: 214 MAB2</strong></p><p><strong>Clinic Schedule</strong></p><p><strong>Mon to Fri except Wed &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10AM - 12NN &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12NN - 2PM</strong></p><p><strong>Sat &nbsp; &nbsp; by appointment</strong></p><p>If you need to verify this or may need to talk to me, you may reach me through my cellphone 09176285021 or the clinic phone number.</p><p>Thank you very much.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>Dr. Buenaventura Ramos, Jr.</p>', '04/03/2017 09:27:08 am', 'read', 'Done'),
