(2040, 'audrey trozo', '0564066483', 'awdrei_trozo@yahoo.com', 'DUbai', 'AE', 'info', 'INQUIRY FOR BREAST SURGERY', '<p>Hi, I am currently working in &nbsp;Dubai. I have multiple cyst in my breast since 2011. When i had my check up here last Aug 2016, i had 2 large size cyst which they did FNAB on the left only. Thats my second FNAB on that cyst and they&nbsp;took&nbsp;52ml fluid on that cyst alone. Now, i&nbsp;am set to go for another follow up check up here since i can feel the bump again and its causing me discomfort and slight tenderness.</p><p>Here&#39;s the report says last aug 2016:</p><p><strong>Conclusion</strong><br />Both breasts are of Category 2 is &lsquo;benign finding (s)&rsquo; grouped into Cysts or Fibrocystic entity. Right breast has large cyst&nbsp;of size 3.50cm x 1.40cm located between 10 o&rsquo; clock to 12 o&rsquo; clock position and left breast has largest cyst of size 8cm x&nbsp;3cm located between 9 o&rsquo; clock to 3 o&rsquo; clock position. Correlate clinically.</p><p>I am thinking maybe its best to remove the cyst since it keeps coming back. But i dont want to do it here. Many still suggest that I should&nbsp;have it done in my own country.</p><p>One of my concern why i have sent this email is since i have insurance here, i want to make sure &nbsp;if the operation is covered. I had asked my insurance advisor and she told me that whoever i chose to do my surgery and which hospital, I should ask an advise from the doctor that it should be remove including&nbsp;the total cost estimate of the surgery (cost til discharge the hospital) so she can forward that to the insurance company for approval. If its approved, the registered hospital and doctor can only do the surgery otherwise the approval will be forfieted.&nbsp;</p><p>Since it will be costly for me to go back home and meet the surgeon for the same request, I am checking if its possible if I can only show my reports through email&nbsp;to you and request the cost estimate for the said surgery.</p><p>Thank you and Im hoping to receive your feedback as soon as possible.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Audrey Trozo</p>', '04/09/2017 05:18:44 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
