(2048, 'Joseph Raven', '7025085200', 'hepatitis@conferenceseries.net', 'London', 'GB', 'info', '5th World Congress on Hepatitis & Liver Diseases', '<p>To</p><p>CEBU DOCTORS&#39; UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL,</p><p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><br />\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings><br />\n  <o:AllowPNG/><br />\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings><br />\n</xml><![endif]--></p><p>Greetings from Hepatitis 2017 London, UK.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>5th World Congress on Hepatitis and Liver Diseases honored to propose you the Mutual Collaboration proposal to develop and share the latest advancements in the field of Hepatitis and Liver Diseases at International level.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We would be glad to inform and invite at the esteemed &ldquo;5th World Congress on Hepatitis and Liver Diseases&rdquo; going to be held in London, UK during August 10-12, 2017. The Hepatitis 2017 Conference aims at bringing all the eminent working in the related field at London so as to share their achievements in front of the global audience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Opportunities</strong></p><p>Branding Opportunities</p><p>Sponsorship Opportunities</p><p>Exhibition Opportunities</p><p>You can organize Workshop</p><p>Sharing Organization information on Websites</p><p>Free Media Partnering Opportunities</p><p>Reduced Registration Prices on Registration and Accommodation</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For more details of the conference proceedings and organizing committee members, kindly visit the official website at: <a href=\"http://hepatitis.conferenceseries.com/\">http://hepatitis.conferenceseries.com/</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We would appreciate your response for the proposal concerned so that we can discuss the proceeding steps in detail.</p><p>For any further details required do not hesitate to mail for assistance.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Awaiting for your prompt and supportive response</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><br />\n <w:WordDocument><br />\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View><br />\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom><br />\n  <w:Track