(2145, 'Praveen Kumar', '3022316756', 'glaucoma@ophthalmologyconferences.com', 'Bangkok', 'TH', 'info', 'Invitation for Ophthalmology and Glaucoma conference, Bangkok', '<p>It is with great pleasure that we invite you to participate in the <strong>17th Global Ophthalmology, Optometry and Glaucoma Conference </strong>to be held at <strong>Bangkok, Thailand</strong> from <strong>November 2-4, 2017</strong>.<br />&nbsp;</p><p>Ophthalmology conference would lay a platform for the interaction between experts around the world and aims in accelerating scientific discoveries. The main theme of the conference is &ldquo;<strong>Enlightening the vision range in ophthalmology</strong>&rdquo;. Ophthalmology conference is a remarkable event which brings together a unique and international mix of large and medium companies, leading universities and research institutions and hospitals in the field of Ophthalmology, Optometry and Glaucoma.<br /><!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br /><!--[endif]--></p>', '05/15/2017 03:47:21 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
