(2172, 'Mitchell Lopez', '6508894686', 'worlddermatology@dermatologyconference.org', 'Dubai', 'VI', 'info', 'Conference Invitaton from World Dermatology 2017', '<p><strong>&quot;</strong><a href=\"http://worlddermatology.conferenceseries.com/\"><strong>17</strong><strong>th</strong>&nbsp;<strong>World Dermatology Congress</strong></a><strong>&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;welcomes all the attendees, speakers, sponsor&rsquo;s and other research expertise from all over the world which is going to be held during &nbsp;<strong>September 25-26</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>2017</strong>&nbsp;in&nbsp;<strong>Dubai, UAE.</strong>&nbsp;We are very much honoured to invite you all to exchange and share your views and experience on the<a href=\"http://worlddermatology.conferenceseries.com/\">&nbsp;World Dermatology</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://worlddermatology.conferenceseries.com/\">Congress</a><strong>.</strong>&nbsp;Dermatology&nbsp;has evolved into one of the most dynamic specialties in medicine.&nbsp;Dermatology&nbsp;is also dedicated to correct the appearance disorders. Indeed, the&nbsp;skin, the largest organ of the human body, is often a place of disease.&nbsp;Skin&nbsp;exposure to environment influences and its importance to the good-looking and well-being requires extra care that can be provided by&nbsp;Dermatology.</p>', '06/01/2017 01:18:08 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
