(2191, 'Jon Frantsvog', '7012903149', 'frantsvog@ndsupernet.com', 'Dickinson, ND', 'US', 'women', 'Seeking physician referral for woman\'s health', '<p>Greetings from the United States<br /><br />I am the CEO of a heathcare facility in the US. My girlfriend is a lifelong resident of Mandaue, 24 year old single female who is in generally good health. Like so many in the Philippines, she has had a less than optimal diet, few preventative services (basic dental,, well child exams, immunizations), or other routine professional health care, and has never had a comprehensive health examination. &nbsp; I&#39;m seeking the names and credentials of physicians who specialize in internal medicine and who have an interest in women&#39;s health and/or are dual boarded in Internal Medice and&nbsp;gynecology. &nbsp;The purpose of this referral is to provide her with choices for a physician to provide her with an age and history appropriate comprehensive examination (including pertinent labs and other studies) to determine her overall health condition, as well as provide suggestions for follow up and/or treatment for any identified problems or deficits, and a recommended course of follow up for general health maintenance. &nbsp;I know your organization has an Executive Health program - and realize that you may recommend this course as an initial comprehensive screen, An estimated cost projection for the requested service would also be appreciated.<br /><br />In advance, thank you for your time and assistance. &nbsp;Please reply via email address provided with this contact.<br /><br />Sincerely,<br /><br />Jon Frantsvog</p>', '06/06/2017 10:43:19 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
