(2232, 'Darls San Miguel', '09178697424', 'darlsfarrah@gmail.com', 'Cebu', 'PH', 'Admin', 'CT SCAN- Very Bad  Service ', '<p>Dear Admin,</p><p>Good day! I would like to express my disappointment to your CT Scan Service in Cebu Doctors Hospital. &nbsp;We have experienced the worst service specifically in the reliability of your staff and timeliness of results.&nbsp;</p><p>My grandmother was admitted and initially assessed as having a stroke. We were considering to avail of the charity (free CT SCAN) but since the test is urgent we looked for a way to pay instead of waiting for that. The incharge told us that once we pay the patient will be transported same day for the scan. But unfortunately what she said was a BIG LIE. So they informed us after paying that it would take days for them to get the patient for the scan. The condition was assessed to be progressive, and the doctor cannot give the specific medicine unless he sees the result. So we spent again for the patient to be transported through ERUF around 1AM this morning. The night duty in charge told us to&nbsp;check with them after&nbsp;lunch for the result. But now when I called she said again to call back tomorrow morning. How much more do we need to wait? We spent to expedite the process but then the same thing it&nbsp;still takes too long. &nbsp;</p><p>The patient could progress to a possible worst condition since we are waiting for this.We have expected a good service as&nbsp;the hospital name itself says Cebu Doctors (a prestigious healthcare institution).&nbsp;I just hope someday your lives wont be at stake and you are not waiting for people who lack&nbsp;customer service in every aspect of&nbsp;these words. I hope you can address this as soon as possible.</p>', '06/28/2017 02:44:48 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
