(2383, 'dwight butler', '639282083056', 'yhyndra@yahoo.com', 'Liptong, Bacong, Negros Orietnal', 'PH', 'Admin', 'I am trying to call the numbers listed but my phone can not connect', '<p>Hello,</p><p>I am Dwight Butler, 61, retired living in the Philippines.&nbsp; I had hernia surgery above my belly button last July.&nbsp; For two months this summer i helped care for my aged father and he fell a lot.&nbsp; I had to catch him, a lot.&nbsp; I have re-injured my hernia, but it is only the inch or so, bilaterally directly abouve my belly button.&nbsp; I am retired with heart disease, when I am feeling better, I exercise daily, eat well and I feel really pretty good, but this irritation and pain has me feeling off. I need this repaired so that I can get back to my daily proactive health routines and mantain my health.&nbsp;</p><p>How much is the surgery?</p><p>Is it outpatient as in America?</p><p>When can I have this done?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I really enjoy my life here when i am healthy and this is a problem i need fixed so i can get back to working on being as healthy as I can.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Plz reply promptly with</p><p>1. cell phone contact for the doctor&#39;s office i need to contact or email. (name please)</p><p>2. Answer my above questions.</p><p>3. What hotels are close to your center?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I am sure there is more to know. I will make arrangement to come there after I have spoken to the doctors office.&nbsp; I will also get a clearance from my local heart doctor.</p><p>Thank You</p><p>Dwight Butler</p><p>Yhyndra@yahoo.com</p><p>639 282 083056</p><p>near dumaguete</p>', '08/30/2017 02:56:44 pm', 'read', 'Pending'),
(2384, 'Alex Greenspan', '6502689744', 'breastcancer@nursingmeetings.com', 'Southampton', 'GB', 'Admin', 'A Personal Invitation for Breast Cancer 2018 Conference, Frankfurt, Germany', '<p><strong>Dear Sir/ Madam,</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Greetings from Breast Cancer 2018</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Please consider this mail as important and require your acknowledgement and a humble appeal as well.<br /><br />We cordially invite <strong>&quot;Cebu Doctors&rsquo; University Hospital&quot; </strong>to<strong> </strong>collaborate with us (as Media/Industrial partner) for Breast Cancer 2018 and participate at this event. We wish to share with the excitement and ideas for creation and exchange of knowledge and information in the scientific field through our Conference with your Association members.<br /><br />We are happy to provide you with the following benefits:<br />&bull; Logo and Link of your Association website in the Conference home page<br />&bull; Recognition listing in the final conference program/proceedings<br />&bull; Logo of the Association on the event&rsquo;s banner<br />&bull; Logo on advertising materials, related to the event<br />&bull; Verbal recognition at the Inaugural Ceremony<br />&bull; Opportunity to take over and organize interested scientific track (s) / session (s) if any<br />&bull; Opportunity to organize a <strong>symposia/workshop </strong>for any interested people from your Association<br />&bull; Opportunity to distribute brochures/issues during the event<br />&bull; Special discounts on registration fee to your members<br />&bull; Exclusive discounts to all your members for Journals, Conferences, eBooks</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><em>We would like to extend our proposal in inviting your Researchers &nbsp;as well to share the experience and views on their current research at Breast Cancer 2018.</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Group Discounts Available!!&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </em></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For more details PS: http://breastcancer.conferenceseries.com/<br /><br />International collaborations makes dissemination of knowledge more immense and diversified, and therefore we work&nbsp;together with several national and international Associations by means of which&nbsp;both Associations support each other from a scientific perspective for their mutual benefit.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>All the participants from your Association who take part in the event will get <strong>25% discount on the registration fee.</strong><br />We request you to partner with the conference as it would be a great help in attainment of knowledge for all the budding scientists and all the audience attending the conference.<br /><br />If you need any further information, please do not hesitate to contact us.<br />We look forward for a long lasting scientific relationship with you.<br />Your reply is eagerly awaited by us.<br /><br />Alex Greenspan</p><p>Program Director</p><p>Breast Cancer 2018</p><p>Kemp House,</p><p>152 City Road,</p><p>London, United Kingdom, EC1V 2NX</p><p>T: +1-650-268-9744</p><p>F: +1-650-618-1414</p><p>Email: breastcancer@conferenceseries.net</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '08/30/2017 05:09:37 pm', 'read', 'Done'),
