(2459, 'Dr Michael K Haldorson', '1204880-1773', 'michaelkelgin@gmail.com', 'Fort St John, British Columbia', 'CA', 'info', 'Private Pay MRI during week of October 2nd 2017', '<p>Hello,</p><p>My name is Dr Michael Haldorson and I am a 30M resident physician in general practice in Canada. My internist Dr Karen Humphreys has recommended to me the following scans: Cardiac MRI with Contrast, MR Angiogram of Aortic Arch and Carotids, MR Angiogram of Renal Arteries, MRI Abdomen and Pelvis.</p><p>My clinical situation is one of increasing BP q10mo not controlled by multiple medications, as well as an alternating tachy/brady arrythmia and a L/Carotid Bruit. I am awaiting MR in Canada but the public system is not fast, and recently I have started to develop significantly worsening symptoms with&nbsp;fevers/chills/diaphoresis/palpitations/diarrhea etc. DDX Endocrine Tumor, Infiltrative Cardiac Disease, Vascular Abnormality.&nbsp;</p><p>I will be flying to Cebu this weekend to stay with family and in order to seek urgent private care and diagnostic workup. Please let me know if the requested scans could be arranged for next week and what procedure would be required to arrange said scans. I was previously healthy, no allergies, no diabetes, Creatinine 82 on Sept 23 / 2017.</p><p>Thank you, Dr M Haldorson</p>', '09/28/2017 06:16:28 am', 'read', 'Done'),
