(2675, 'Mitchell Lopez', '6508894686', 'worlddermatology@dermatologyconference.org', 'Tokyo', 'JP', 'info', 'Conference Invitaton from World Dermatology 2018', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><strong>&quot;</strong><a href=\"http://worlddermatology.conferenceseries.com/\"><strong>19th</strong>&nbsp;<strong>World Dermatology Congress</strong></a><strong>&rdquo;&nbsp;</strong>welcomes all the speakers, delegates (both from academy and business) sponsor&rsquo;s and other research expertise at Tokyo, Japan held during</p><p><strong>May 9-10</strong><strong>,&nbsp;<strong>2018</strong></strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;This conference provides beautiful platform for Dermatology as well as business networking and luxurious stay at Tokyo.</p><p>We are having many sessions among them brief discussion on</p><p>Dermatology, Skin Cancer, Dermatological Diseases, Skin Grafting, Derma-Pathology, Hair Transplantation, Hair Transplant Surgery, Venereology, Contagious Skin Infections, Side effects of cosmetics, Rejuvenation and Resurfacing, Microdermabrasion Treatment, Treatment of Hyperpigmentation, Technology to Treat Melanoma, Aesthetic Surgical Procedures.</p><p>Kindly submit your abstract if you want to attend as a Speaker.</p><p>It would be great if you are willing to attend the Congress kindly contact us at the earliest. For further queries kindly revert back to us, we will be very happy to assist you all the time.</p>', '12/18/2017 06:50:04 pm', 'unread', 'Pending'),
