(2693, 'Joseph Raven', '7025085202', 'hepatitis@gastroconferences.com', 'Henderson', 'US', 'info', ' 6th World Congress on Hepatitis & Liver Diseases', '<p><strong>To</strong></p><p>CEBU DOCTORS&#39; UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL<strong>,</strong></p><p>Greetings from Hepatitis 2018!</p><p>On behalf of Organizing Committee, we would like to invite you to join 6th World Congress on Hepatitis and Liver Diseases, going to be held in Dublin, Ireland during June 18-20, 2018. The theme of the conference is <strong>&quot;Raising global awareness on screening and prevention of hepatitis.&quot;</strong></p><p><strong>Opportunities</strong></p><p>Speaker/Poster Opportunities</p><p>You can organize Workshop</p><p>Reduced Registration Prices on Registration and Accommodation</p><p>For more details of the conference, kindly visit the official website at: https://hepatitis.conferenceseries.com/</p><p>We would appreciate your response for the proposal concerned so that we can discuss the proceeding steps in detail.</p><p><strong>Joseph Raven</strong></p><p>Program Director | Hepatitis 2018</p><p>Kemp House, 152 City Road, London EC1V 2NX, UK</p><p>Toll Free: +1-800-014-8923</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/03/2018 10:07:25 pm', 'unread', 'Pending'),
(2694, 'norman r hahn', '14077567427', 'drodad22@gmail.com', 'orlando/Florida', 'US', 'info', 'Cardiovascular information', '<p>My name is Norman Hahn.&nbsp; I reside in Orlando, Florida..&nbsp; I am a heart patient here in Orlando.&nbsp; My cardiologist is planning to inset a pace maker for me in the near future.&nbsp; When I told her that I was planning an extended trip to Cebu later this year, she wanted to implant a device that your doctors were familiar with so that if I experienced any complications while there, you could help me.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>If you can help me with information regarding pacemaker devices that you are familiar with,&nbsp;you may respond to this email or you may phone my wife, Lolita Bonjoc Hahn, at 407-701-3977.&nbsp; &nbsp;I do appreciate your help. Sincerely,</p><p>Norman Hahn</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/04/2018 10:30:18 am', 'read', 'Pending'),
