(2699, 'Maria Bercasio', '12045836211', 'maridol_ruy@yahoo.ca', 'Winnipeg', 'CA', 'info', 'Free Medical and Dental Mission for Barangay Ablayan and Maloray, Dalaguete, Province of Cebu', '<p>We are Alumni from Muntinlupa National High School Class 78 &nbsp;who will be celebrating our 40th Anniversary.. In this regards we have chosen barangay Ablayan and Maloray as beneficiaries of our free Medical and Dental and Livelihood programs to help the people there to alleviate there health, social and economic condition after the closing of mining industry in the area that leaves the people poorer condition.</p><p>in lieu of this may we invite atleast 2 medical practitioners and 1 dentist from your hospital to join our mission to render free medical/dental check up to parents and their&nbsp;children. And to provide them with needed medicines, feeding programs for school children and Livelihood Training for jobless parents.</p><p>We can provide formal request if you need it.</p><p>thank you very much and looking forward of your help to this humble approach to help the poor and deprived families in the Province of Cebu..</p><p>Thnak you very much,</p><p>Maria Bercasio</p><p>Organizing Committe</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '01/08/2018 09:18:27 am', 'read', 'Done'),
