(5, 'CDUH @ 42 years of Caring and Touching Lives', '2014-08-18', 'Admin', '<p class=\"indent\">Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital commemorated its <strong>42<sup>nd</sup> Founding Anniversary</strong> last August 18, 2014. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">The celebration was started by offering a Thanksgiving Mass at 10:30 A.M in CDUH Sacred Heart Chapel presided by Msgr.  Roberto \"Boy\" Alesna with the assistance of our very own Chapel priest Fr. Armand Orehuela, our LGC Sisters headed by Sr. Miguela Niala and CDUH Chaplain Interns. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">The daughters of the President and Chairman of the Board, and the Founder of CDUH, Dr. Potenciano \"Jun\" Larrazabal, Jr. were assigned as the Readers; Mrs. Mia Carcel as the First Reader while Mrs. Bettina Anne L. Veloso as the Prayers of the Faithful. On the other hand, Engr. Oscar Tuason, Hospital Administrator together with Dr. Enrico B. Gruet, Vice- President of Academic Affairs was assigned as the \"Responsorial Psalm\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">The Mass has partaken by the employees, Medical and Non-Medical Staffs, Administrative Heads and other distinguishing guests, as they joined together to celebrate Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital\'s 42<sup>nd</sup> Founding Anniversary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">The main celebration and Lunch was followed after the Mass, at CDUH Conference Rooms A and B with entertainments and commotions as we honor and salute the Board Members, Medical Experts and Employees who made a remarkable impact in the institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">The commemoration has started by an Invocation leaded by CDUH Chorale and followed by the singing of Philippine National Anthem.  Engr. Oscar A. Tuason shared his gratitude as he takes on the Words of Welcome. After the very last word of Engr. Tuason, colorful balloons were cut symbolizing prosperity and achievement.  The Blessing of Food by Fr. Armand Orehuela followed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">After 30 minutes, CDUH Chorale serenaded us through their Song Number entitled \"May Ibong Kakanta Kanta\".  Each and every one looked dynamic and bubbly amid their classy outfits.  Afterward, Awarding Ceremony followed. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr. with the assistance of his wife, Mrs. Zenaida S.D. Larrazabal were requested to hand over the certificates to the awardees through the helping hands of Mrs. Chadelsa Binondo, Human Resources Director and Mrs. Edna Caballero, Nursing Service Department Head, while Engr. Oscar A. Tuason was asked to read out the names. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">All the awardees from CDUH Service Award, Perfect Attendance, and as well as CDU Loyalty Award were astonishingly happy and excited to receive their cash and certificates. All their hard works paid off. Yes! They\'re all absolutely deserved it. Couldn\'t agree more!</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">Another Song Number of Ms. Silvia Rikka Aberilla entertained us with a contemporary song entitled \"Jesus takes the wheel\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">Dr. Potenciano S.D. Larrazabal III, son of Dr. and Mrs. Larrazabal, conferred an inspirational Anniversary Message and followed by Dr. Enrico B. Gruet\'s Closing Remarks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">The masters of ceremony were young professionals Dr. Karl Suarez and Ms. Clarice Fritz Caliwatan. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"indent\">Indeed, this year\'s Founding Anniversary is a further milestones and accomplishment. Looking forward to another more prosperous year!</p>\r\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\">\r\n<p class=\"center\"><strong>42. A Blissful 42 years of Service!</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"center\"><strong>Happy Anniversary, Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital!</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/img2.jpg\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"multiimages\" data-title=\"Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital 42nd Anniversary\">\r\n        <img src=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/thumbs/img2.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail img-responsive\" />\r\n    </a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/img3.jpg\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"multiimages\" data-title=\"Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital 42nd Anniversary\">\r\n        <img src=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/thumbs/img3.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail img-responsive\" />\r\n    </a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/img4.jpg\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"multiimages\" data-title=\"Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital 42nd Anniversary\">\r\n        <img src=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/thumbs/img4.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail img-responsive\" />\r\n    </a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/img5.jpg\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"multiimages\" data-title=\"Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital 42nd Anniversary\">\r\n        <img src=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/thumbs/img5.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail img-responsive\" />\r\n    </a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/img6.jpg\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"multiimages\" data-title=\"Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital 42nd Anniversary\">\r\n        <img src=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/thumbs/img6.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail img-responsive\" />\r\n    </a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/img7.jpg\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"multiimages\" data-title=\"Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital 42nd Anniversary\">\r\n        <img src=\"../../images/anniversary/42/mass/thumbs/img7.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail img-responsive\" />\r\n    </a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"../../images/anniversary/42/main/img1.jpg\" data-toggl