(9, 'CDUH: We Lead to Serve Feeding Program', '2015-03-02', 'Admin', '<p>With the theme entitled, CDUH: We Lead To Serve, Cebu Doctors&rsquo; University Hospital organized its first community-based outreach program for the year 2015.</p><p>The 200 malnourished children at elementary level living in Barangay Kamputhaw, Cebu were benefitted through a feeding program spearheaded by Cebu Doctors&rsquo; University Hospital Administration and with the help of the Social Worker, Volunteers and the CO of Barangay Kamputhaw. It was held last February 28, 2015 at Barangay Kamputhaw Gymnasium.</p><p>The main goal of the program was to serve and value the health of children in the community.</p><p>Participating children were weighed after to monitor the progress and success of the program.</p><p>Everybody wore smiles on their faces. The best feeling you get is when you help the people in your community and make them happy. <strong>Remember: &ldquo;Small acts when multiplied by millions of people, can transform the world&rdquo;.</strong></p><p>In behalf of Cebu Doctors&rsquo; University Hospital, we would like to extend our warm thank you to the officials of Barangay Kamputhaw for making this program put into reality.</p><p>This will be a fresh start and still looking forward for more outreach activity.</p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/CDUH_We_Lead_to_Serve_Feeding_Program.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH: WE LEAD TO SERVE FEEDING PROGRAM\" alt=\"CDUH: WE LEAD TO SERVE FEEDING PROGRAM\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/thumbs/CDUH_We_Lead_to_Serve_Feeding_Program.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n		  </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feeding (1).jpg\" da