(13, 'CDUH Family 1 - DAYLYMPIC 2015', '2015-08-16', 'Admin', '<p>In celebration of the 43rd Founding Anniversary, CDUH Employees had joined together as one, held last August 16, 2015, which entitled &ldquo;<strong>CDUH Family 1-DayLympic 2015&rdquo;</strong>.</p><p>The first part of the event was a Eucharistic Celebration held at 7:15 AM, in CDUH Sacred Heart Chapel and followed by the Program Proper at D&rsquo; Family Park, Talamban, Cebu City.</p><p>There were more than 800 bonafide staff who participated and witnessed this momentous activity.&nbsp;</p><p>The Committee was composed by the all administrative heads from the various participating teams, headed by Engr. Dennis A. Labus, Commissioner, and Ms. Aurora Ramos, Asst. Commissioner.</p><p>The participating teams were divided into 7 with each designated colors:</p><p><strong>RED TEAM</strong> &ndash; Nursing Services Team A</p><p><strong>PINK TEAM</strong> &ndash; Administrative, B.O, HR, Med Rec</p><p><strong>GREEN TEAM</strong> &ndash; Engineering, Housekeeping, Dietary</p><p><strong>ORANGE TEAM</strong> &ndash; Pulmonary, Radiation, Radiology, Nuclear Medicine, Center for Women</p><p><strong>LAVENDER TEAM</strong> &ndash; Linen and Laundry, Cardiology, Rehab, Pharmacy</p><p><strong>BLUE TEAM</strong> &ndash; Laboratory, Admitting</p><p><strong>YELLOW TEAM</strong> &ndash; Nursing Services Team B</p><p>The program was started by a Parade of Colors and the Acknowledgement of Participating Teams, followed by the Invocation and Singing of the Philippine National Anthem led by the CDUH Chorale. &nbsp;Oath of Sportsmanship by Ms. Aurora Ramos was followed after the Lighting of Torch by Mr. Arian Paul Veloso. &nbsp;</p><p>Cheer Dance Competition was went after, judged by Ms. Catherine F. Vestil.</p><p>Each team individually showed their talents, creativity and their gloss of elegance. Red Team was announced as the CHAMPION; PINK TEAM was the 1st runner up, GREEN TEAM was the 2nd runner up; YELLOW TEAM was the 3rd runner up.</p><p>Other List of Games were:</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Sangkayaw</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Buko Relay</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Japanese Doll</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Relay Inside a Hoolahoop</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Balloon Sandwich</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Carry the Queen</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Balloon Bursting</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Ball/Tire Roller Relay</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Marble Relay</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->10.&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Roll the Ball with Talong Relay</p><p><!--[if !supportLists]-->11.&nbsp;&nbsp; <!--[endif]-->Water Relay</p><p>The OVER-ALL WINNERS FOR THIS YEAR&rsquo;S CDUH FAMILY 1-DAYLMPIC:</p><p>CHAMPION &ndash; ORANGE TEAM</p><p>1ST RUNNER UP &ndash; RED TEAM</p><p>2ND RUNNER UP- GREEN TEAM</p><p>3rd RUNNER UP- LAVENDER TEAM</p><p>4TH RUNNER UP &ndash; BLUE TEAM</p><p>5TH RUNNER UP &ndash; PINK TEAM</p><p>6TH RUNNER UP &ndash; YELLOW TEAM</p><p><strong>Congratulations to all the winners! It was very remarkable, indeed.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/familyday1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH FAMILY 1-DAYLYMPIC 2015\" alt=\"CDUH FAMILY 1-DAYLYMPIC 2015\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/thumbs/familyday1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n   