(14, 'CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM', '2015-08-26', 'Admin', '<p><strong>FREE ADMISSION!</strong> The <strong> CDUH</strong> Chorale leaded by Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator has hit ground running to present another fine Annual Thanksgiving and Praise concert, held last Thursday, November 26, 2015 at CDUH Conference Room. </p><br>\r\n<p>The concert began with a sumptuous dinner at 7:00 pm. </p><br>\r\n<p>The said event was thoughtful, engaging and even inspiring, emphasizing the choral music and featuring the various praise and worship soundtracks and selected ABBA songs, as has been the custom for this event. </p><br>\r\n<p><strong>Thanksgiving</strong>, or <strong>Thanksgiving Day</strong>, is a harvest festival and an important public holiday which is celebrated on the fourth Thursday in November in the United States.</p><br>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/tg2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM\" alt=\"CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/thumbs/tg2.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"clearfix\"></div> \r\n	</div>                    \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#fff;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.1605968799676993.1073741834.1411493215791220&type=3\">Click here for more Photos...</a>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div><br /><br />', 'upload/CDUH_Medical_Mission2.jpg'),
(15, 'CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY', '2015-09-29', 'Admin', '<p>CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\r\n</p>\r\n<p >YOUR HOME</p><p>\r\nAugust 21, 2015 – Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital celebrated its 43rd Anniversary with its “Fellowship Dinner” for the Medical Staff held at the Grand Convention Center.</p><p>\r\nThe medical staff gathered together to rejoice this year’s anniversary wearing their dazzling attire accompanying the theme of “A Touch of Royal Blue”.</p><p >  \r\nDr. Enrico B. Gruet welcomed the guests with an inspiring speech.  Dinner was followed after. </p><p>\r\nDr. Yong Larrazabal gave a toast to express his gratitude to all the medical staff, “The hospital would not exist without very good and competent doctors”.</p><p>\r\nThe night wouldn’t get better as the different departments presented their production number:</p><p>\r\n</p><p><b>THE DEPARTMENT OF SURGERY</b> presented a song number with musical instruments  </p><p>\r\n<b>THE DEPARTMENT OF INTERNAL MEDICINE</b> presented a “hip-hop” dance number as well as <b>THE DEPARTMENT OF ANESTHESIA. </b></p><p>\r\n<b>THE DEPARTMENT OF OB</b> presented an amusing song number.</p><p>\r\n<b>THE DEPARTMENT OF PEDIA</b> presented a play and a dance number where in they were wearing a superhero costumes.</p><p>\r\n<b>THE DEPARTMENT OF OPTHALMOLOGY</b> led by Dr. Yong who turned to be the singing doctor that night, while others were dancing in a tune of “I stop the world, and melt with you” song.</p><p>\r\nOur very own <b>BOARD OF DIRECTORS</b> and the Department Chairs jived into the music of Bruno Mars – “Uptown Funk” who energetically hopped in the dancing floor. </p><p>\r\nThe crowd was astonished by a special guest, Mr. Jun Polistico, known as “The Golden Voice of Asia” - who serenaded them with classic songs.</p><p> \r\nIt was a fun-filled night with loads of entertainment, laughter, good food, door prizes and great camaraderie for CDUH Medical Staff.</p><p>\r\nTruly, CDUH is Your HOME, and Our HOME. It is the HOME for everybody!!</b></p>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\" alt=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\" alt=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU2.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                 <a href=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU3.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\" alt=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU3.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU4.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\" alt=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL 43rd ANNIVERSARY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU4.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n          \r\n        \r\n             <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                 <a href=\"../../images/anniv43/CDU5.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CEBU DOCTORS’ UNIVERSITY 