(16, 'THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT', '2015-12-08', 'Admin', '<p><strong>FREE ADMISSION!</strong> The <strong> CDUH</strong> Chorale leaded by Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator has hit ground running to present another fine Annual Thanksgiving and Praise concert, held last Thursday, November 26, 2015 at CDUH Conference Room. </p><br>\r\n<p>The concert began with a sumptuous dinner at 7:00 pm. </p><br>\r\n<p>The said event was thoughtful, engaging and even inspiring, emphasizing the choral music and featuring the various praise and worship soundtracks and selected ABBA songs, as has been the custom for this event. </p><br>\r\n<p><strong>Thanksgiving</strong>, or <strong>Thanksgiving Day</strong>, is a harvest festival and an important public holiday which is celebrated on the fourth Thursday in November in the United States.</p><br>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/tg2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT\" alt=\"THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/thumbs/tg2.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/tg3.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT\" alt=\"THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/thumbs/tg3.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/tg4.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT\" alt=\"THANKSGIVING AND PRAISE CONCERT\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/thumbs/tg4.jpg\" class=\"img-re