(17, 'RADIOLOGY DEPARTMENT BLESSING', '2016-02-12', 'Admin / Radiology Department', '<p>Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital’s Radiology Department now offers the new innovation in liver disease management.<strong> FibroScan®</strong> uses state of the art fibrosis and steatosis quantification with the most advanced non-invasive technology.</p>\r\n<p>The Department was also had a blessing of its New Ultrasound Room, New improved CT-Scan Room, Newly Room to house the MRI machine and New Location of Center for Women. </p>\r\n<p>It was blessed by Rev. Fr. Arman Orehuela and LGC Sisters, and well-attended by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal & Mrs. Zenaida S.D. Larrazabal, Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Dr. Philip S.D. Larrazabal and Dr. Marivic Larrazabal and all Radiology Consultants, Staff and Radiology Department Head Mr. Michael Gasta.</p>\r\n<strong>FibroScan® touch 502</strong> at Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital is the first of its kind in Visayas and Mindanao. For more information, contact us at (032) 255-5555.</p>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/radbless/rad (1).jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH MEDICAL MISSION 2015 (Our Lady of the Sacred Heart Parish)\" alt=\"CDUH MEDICAL MISSION 2015 (Our Lady of the Sacred Heart Parish)\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/radbless/rad (1).jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/radbless/rad (2).jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH MEDICAL MISSION 2015 (Our Lady of the Sacred Heart Parish)\" alt=\"CDUH MEDICAL MISSION 2015 (Our Lady of the Sacred Heart Parish)\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/radbless/rad (2).jpg\" class=\"img-responsive