(20, 'TEAM REWARD AWARDING & RECOGNITION', '2016-05-17', 'ADMIN', '\r\n<p>Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital has established a Team Reward Program, applicable to all areas in the hospital. This program has been designed to foster a spirit of “one for all and all for one” as well as to reinforce organizational values, behaviors and operating principles. </p>\r\n<p>Last 13th of May, the Most Outstanding Team for the Month of April has been recognized. The Nursing Services Office was awarded as the Best Team 1st placer. Runners-up are: Business Office 2 (2nd place) and Housekeeping Department (3rd place).  Each Team has received cash and certificate. </p>\r\n<p>The awards were given by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr., President and Chairman of the Board; Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator, and Mrs. Bettina Veloso, Comptroller. The Recognition was attended by CDUH Admin Circle.</p>\r\n<p>Engr. Tuason said that this kind of program will motivate and enlighten each members of the team to foster team work and dedication. Dr. Larrazabal, Jr. humorously said he will be giving more rewards if the winning team will get 90% of the criteria. </p>\r\n<p>The selection of the recipient for the Team Reward Program was based on the given parameters like Group Attendance, Group Efficiency and etc., and it was mediated by the selection committee. The committee is compromised of the HR Director as the Chairman of the Committee and 7 regular committee members recommended by their respective department to form part in the formulation of the guidelines of this program as well as to act as the Selection Committee.</p>\r\n<p><strong>“Together Everyone Achieves More”   -- Team </strong></p>\r\n<p>Congratulations to all the winners!!</P>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/