(22, 'OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF MAY 2016', '2016-06-09', 'Hr', '<p><strong>OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF MAY 2016</strong></p><br>\r\n<p>June 7, 2016, Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital has recognized another outstanding team. </p>\r\n<p>Business Office 1 (Cashier, Billing and Philhealth Section) got the first place and was awarded as the Best Team for the Month of May.  Other awardees were, Business Office 3 (Audit Section, EDP, Purchasing and Central Service, (2nd place) and Delivery Room and Nursery Sections (3rd place).</p>\r\n<p>The awards were handed by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal., President and Chairman of the Board; Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator and Mrs. Bettina Veloso, Comptroller.</p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/trp/may1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARD PROGRAM: MAY\" alt=\"TEAM REWARD PROGRAM: MAY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/trp/may1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/trp/may2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARD PROGRAM: MAY\" alt=\"TEAM REWARD PROGRAM: MAY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/trp/may2.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/trp/may3.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARD PROGRAM: MAY\" alt=\"TEAM REWARD PROGRAM: MAY\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/trp/may3.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> 			  \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n           