(23, 'CANADA DAY 2016', '2016-06-30', 'Admin', '<p>Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital celebrated the 2-day Canada Day at Ayala Mall, Activity Center-- 3rd time in arrow last June 29-30, 2016. Following the success of the Canada Trade Fairs last 2014 and 2015!</p>\r\n<p>The program was started at 10:00 AM, by opening remarks of Ms. Cora dela Cruz. Executive Director of CanCham and an introductory message of Mr. Felix “Boy” Tiukinhoy, Chairperson, Advisory Committee of theCanCham Cebu Chapter.</p>\r\n<p>We offered FREE SERVICES such as: <strong>FREE CAPILLARY BLOOD SUGAR, FREE BLOOD TYPING & FREE BLOOD PRESSURE MONITORING and DIET COUNSELING.</strong></P>\r\n<p><strong>Another achievement Happy 149th Birthday Canada!</strong></p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/canada/1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CANDA DAY 2016\" alt=\"CANDA DAY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/canada/1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/canada/2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CANDA DAY 2016\" alt=\"CANDA DAY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/canada/2.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/canada/3.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CANDA DAY 2016\" alt=\"CANDA DAY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/canada/3.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>  \r\n			<div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/canada/4.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CANDA DAY 2016\" alt=\"CANDA