(24, 'OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JUNE 2016', '2016-06-21', 'Admin', '\r\nOUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JUNE 2016\r\n\r\n<p>July 20, 2016, Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital has recognized another winning team for the team rewards.</p>\r\n<P>Pharmacy Department got the <strong>1st place</strong>, average rate of 70.33 with the highlights of: Perfect Score on Attendance with no Absences; Perfect Score in Supply Savings; No workplace Injury; Perfect Score in Safe Patient/Customer Care Perfect Score in Compliance to Policies both Minor and Major Offenses.</P>\r\n<p>Business Office 2 got the <strong>2nd place</strong>>, average rate of 69.20 with the highlights of: Perfect Score on Attendance; No workplace Injury; Perfect Score in Customer Care; Perfect Score in Customer Care; Perfect Score in Customer Care; Perfect Score in Phone Courtesy; Perfect Score in Compliance to Policies both Minor and Major Offenses.</p>\r\n<p>Admin/HR, Medical Records and Linen Department got the <strong>3rd place, average rate of 67.00</strong> with the highlights of:  No workplace Injury; Perfect Score in Safe Patient/Client/ Customer; No Sickness Occurrence; Perfect Score in Phone Courtesy; Perfect Score in Team Effort and Organization; Perfect Score in Compliance to Policies both Minor and Major Offenses.</p>\r\n<p>The awards were handed by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr. (President and Chairman of the Board), and Engr. Oscar A. Tuason (Hospital Administrator).  It was also attended by the Administrative Circle.</p><br>\r\n<p><strong>Congratulations to all the winning teams!</strong></p> \r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/trp/junecover.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JUNE 2016\" alt=\"OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JUNE 2016\">\r\n 