(25, 'EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016', '2016-08-14', 'admin, Photo by : Leo V. Ruelan', '<p>August 14, 2016 (Sunday) Cebu Doctor’s University Hospital were rejoicing its 2nd Employee’s Appreciation Day with the Theme: 44th and Beyond in line with the Anniversary Celebration. More than 400 employees were participated and joined the “one-of-the favorite” day of the year. </p>\r\n<p>The 1st part of the program was the Eucharistic Celebration which presided by Fr. Martin Okafer-Illozue. The second part was the Program Proper, Zumba Warm-up Exercise and the Games Competition. </p>\r\n<p>Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal and Mrs. Zenaida S.D. Larrazabal, Dr. Enrico B. Gruet and Engr. Oscar A. Tuason were there to eyewitness the momentous activity.</p>\r\n<p>There were six (6) teams with each designated colors competed the major and minor games.</p>\r\n<p>Team 6 Black proclaimed as the 6th placer; Team 3 Green as the 5th placer; Team 2 Orange as the 4th placer; Team 5 Blue as the 3rd placer; Team 1 Yellow as the 2nd placer and OVER-ALL CHAMPION 1st placer is TEAM 4 RED.</p>\r\n<p>All the winning teams will be awarded on August 19, 2016.</p>\r\n<p>It was a fun-filled day activity for all the participants.</p>\r\n<p>Happy Employee’s Appreciation Day to all!</p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/empap/1.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016\" alt=\"EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/empap/1.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/empap/2.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016\" alt=\"EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016\">\r\n   