(26, 'ANNIVERSARY CELEBRATION', '2016-08-30', 'Admin', '<p>Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital celebrated its 44th Founding Anniversary Celebration with a theme: “44th and Beyond”. </p>\r\n<p>In line with this celebration, the hospital has organized series of activities such as:</p>\r\n<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><strong>August 15 , 2016 </strong></li>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li><p>Poster Making Contest for a Cause with the theme: “<strong>44 years of Quality Healthcare Delivery… The Way Forward.</strong>” 7 entries were participated and all the entries were part of the Anniversary’s Art Exhibit for a Cause and were available for display in the hospital’s lobby. The amount raised from the entries was used for the indigent patients on Medical Mission (August 20).</p></li>\r\n        <li><p>Photography Contest with the theme: “<strong>Alaga’t Kalinga: The CDUH Way of Caring and Nurturing Patients</strong>”.</p></li>\r\n        <li>There was an Opening Mass presided by Fr. Arman Orehuela and sponsored by the HR/ADMIN Department.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><strong>August 19, 2016</strong></li>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li><p><strong>SHARE A GIFT TO A PATIENT</strong> - Complete Admission Kits were given to the 1st 44 PAYWARD patients admitted last August 19 and fruit of baskets were also given to the 1st 44 patients admitted in the PRIVATE ROOMS.</p></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/44aniv/1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016\" alt=\"EMPLOYEE’S APPRECIATION DAY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/44aniv/1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a hre