(27, 'CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2016', '2016-08-30', 'Admin', '<p>With a thankful heart, Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital had their Medical Mission last August 20, 2016, at Our Mother of Perpetual Help Parish in line celebration of the 44TH Founding Anniversary.</p>\r\n<p>More than 450 patients were benefitted and given free medical, pediatric and optical services. Check-up for medical were given to 101 adults and Pedia for 91. One hundred fifteen (115) were also given free reading glasses, ECG Test for 76 patients and 84 patients for CBS & Blood Typing. Free snacks were also given to the all patients.</p>\r\n<P>We also had a raffle draw for all the patients.</P>\r\n<p>The medical mission was supported by Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital (CDUH) Administrator and partners from different drug companies. Manpower services were provided by volunteer staff from CDUH and volunteers from the Redemptorist Parish. Doctors, interns, optometrists, nurses, pharmacy staff, social workers and administrative staff were the volunteers for this activity.</p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/medmisaug/1.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2016\" alt=\"CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/medmisaug/1.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/medmisaug/2.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2016\" alt=\"CDUH SERVES THE COMMUNITY: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/medmisaug/2.