(28, 'CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016', '2016-09-08', 'Admin / hr', '<p>August 31, 2016- The Top 3 Outstanding Teams for the Month of July has been recognized. The Business Office 2 composing (Receivable, Credit and Collection, Payroll Section, Financial Management) was awarded as the Best Team 1st placer with the average rate of 72.67%. Runners up are:  Radiology Department (2nd place) with the average score of 71.50% and Nursing Service Office (3rd place) with the average score of 70.90%.</p>\r\n<p>The awards were handed by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr., President and Chairman of the Board and Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator. The Recognition was also attended by CDUH Admin Circle.</p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/otp/1.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016\" alt=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/otp/1.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/otp/2.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016\" alt=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/otp/2.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/otp/3.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016\" alt=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF JULY 2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/otp/3.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumb