(29, 'HMO/INSURANCE UPDATE MEETING', '2016-09-28', 'admin / hr', '<p>Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital organized this year’s HMO/INSURANCE UPDATE MEETING, held at CDUH Conference Room A last September 20, 2016. Registration was started at 11:30 AM. There were more than 50 participants from the different HMO and INSURANCE Companies, CDUH Representatives, and other sister hospitals like NGH, SGH AND MDH. Administrators from the different hospitals mentioned, Dr. Enrico B. Gruet also joined and celebrated the event. After Lunch, Engr. Tuason gave his speech addressing on to serve the patients is not just about the facility but it is for the “pleasant experience”.  He also mentioned the services of CDUH like Hyperbaric Centre (in which CDUH is the only hospital-based hyperbaric chamber in Cebu), Minimally Invasive Center, Heart Center and HMO Help Desk. The Open Forum was next in line where the comments, questions and suggestions were raised and brought in. </p>\r\n<p>Top 3 highest HMO and INSURANCE Contributors were recognized: Intellicare got the highest place for the HMO Category and Asian Life and General Assurance Corporation got the highest place for the INSURANCE Category. Runners-up for the HMO Category are: 2nd is the Maxicare Health Care, 3rd is Medicard Phils, Inc. While runners-up for INSURANCE CATEGORY: 2nd is Avega Managed Care, Inc and 3rd is the Insular Life Assurance Co. Ltd.</p>\r\n<p>Mr. Chito Recamadas of INTELLICARE and Ms. Lucille Amendes of ASIAN LIFE had given their inspiring and thank you message. Words of Gratitude by Dr. Enrico B. Gruet followed then. Tokens and Certificate of Attendance were also handed to the participants.</p>\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/hmo/1.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"HMO/INSURANCE UPDATE MEETING\">\r\n    