(32, 'TEAM REWARD WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF AUGUST 2016', '2016-11-01', 'admin', '<p>We had recognized again the OUTSTANDING TEAM for the Month of August, and yet this time, it was divided by two (2) categories: NON-NURSING AND NURSING.</p>\r\n<p>For the Non-Nursing Category: Team 5 composing Business Office 1 ranked first place with the overall rating of 71.20%; Team 6 composing Business Office 2 ranked second place with the overall rating of 71.15% ;  and Team 13 composing Pharmacy ranked third place with the overall rating of 63.70%.</p>\r\n<p>For the Nursing Category: Team 21 composing Delivery Room/Nursery got the highest place with the overall rating of 51.40 % ; Team 29 composing 5A Station got the second highest place with the overall rating of 48.90 % ; and Team 23 composing 2A Station got the third highest place with the overall rating of 47.90%.</p>\r\n<p>The awards were handed by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr., President and Chairman of the Board, Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator and Mrs. Bettina Veloso.</p>\r\n<p>The Recognition was done at CDUH Board Room and it was well-attended by CDUH Admin Circle. </p>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	<div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/otp1/1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF AUGUST  2016\" alt=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF AUGUST  2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/otp1/1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/otp1/2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF AUGUST  2016\" alt=\"CDUH OUTSTANDING TEAM FOR THE MONTH OF AUGUST  2016\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images