(33, 'TEAM REWARD WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF SEPTEMBER 2016', '2016-11-10', 'admin hr', '<p>We had recognized again the OUTSTANDING TEAM for the Month of September.</p>\r\n<p>For the Non-Nursing Category: Team 5 composing Business Office 1 ranked first place with the overall rating of 78.85%; Team 6 composing Business Office 2 ranked second place with the overall rating of 71.10% ;  and Team 13 composing Pharmacy ranked third place with the overall rating of 67.80%.</p>\r\n<p>For the Nursing Category: Team 26 composing 3A and 5B Stations got the highest place with the overall rating of 62.50 % ; Team 29 composing Intensive Care Unit got the second highest place with the overall rating of 57.50 % ; and Team 22 composing Operating and Recovery Rooms got the third highest place with the overall rating of 54.70%.</p>\r\n<p>Commendation to Engineering Department for almost hitting top 3.</p>\r\n<p>The awards were handed by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr., President and Chairman of the Board, Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator and Mrs. Bettina Veloso.</p>\r\n<p>The Recognition was done at CDUH Board Room and it was well-attended by CDUH Admin Circle. </p>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n	                  \r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div><br /><br />\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'gallery/otp1/3.jpg'),
(34, 'CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE', '2016-12-30', 'ADMIN HR', '<strong><p>CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE</p></strong>\n<P>\nLast December 21, 2016, Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital shared bundles of happiness and love to the patients who are admitted in the Payward accommodation (Male, Female and Pediatric). Both female and male were given a basket of food while the Pediatric were given chocolates, toys and other baby stuff. </p>\n<p>The money bought for all the presents given to the patients are came from the proceeds of the SNOWMAN CONTEST AND CHRISTMAS DECORATION CONTEST, where more than 20 departments/sections of CDUH joined and participated. </p>\n<p>HAPPINESS DOESN\'T RESULT FROM WHAT WE GET, BUT WE GIVE.</p>\n<p>Thanks to those who helped to make this activity achievable; to all the people who donated and shared, and for the support of our dear CDUH Administration. \nAnything is possible if you work together as one. </p>\n<p><strong>MERRY CHRISTMAS EVERYONE!!!</strong></p>\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\n    <hr />\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\n    <br />\n	<div id=\"links\">\n            \n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/pasko/1.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE\" alt=\"CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/pasko/1.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/pasko/2.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE\" alt=\"CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/pasko/2.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/pasko/3.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE\" alt=\"CHRISTMAS FOR A CAUSE\">\n                    <img src=\".