(36, 'TEAM REWARD AND RECOGNITION PROGRAM WINNERS’ HIGHLIGHTS FOR MONTH OF FEBRUARY 2017', '2017-02-01', 'Admin / HR', '<strong><p>TEAM REWARDS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF FEBRUARY 2017</p></strong>\n<P>\nThe Most Outstanding Team for the Month of February 2017 has been recognized last Thursday, March 31, 2017 at CDUH Board Room.</p>\n\n<strong><p>For the Non-Nursing Category: Team 5 composing Business Office 1 ranked as 1st place with the average rating of 84.66 %:</p></strong>\n\n<p>Highlights: No Absences and Undertime, No workplace Injury or Accident, Perfect Score in Customer Care, No sickness Incidence, With 5 positive feedbacks, Perfect Score in Phone Courtesy, Perfect Score in Social Responsibility, Perfect Score for both Minor and Major Offense in Compliance to hospital policies.</p>\n\n<strong><p>Runners are up are: Team 7 composing Business Office 3 ranked as 2nd placed with the average rating of 75.93 %.</p></strong>\n\n<p>Highlights: No Absences, No Workplace Injury or Accident, Perfect Score in Customer Care, No Sickness Incidence, With 5 positive feedbacks, Perfect Score in Social Responsibility.</p>\n\n<strong><p>Team 12 composing Laboratory Group 2 ranked as 3rd place with the average rating of 71.60%. </p></strong>\n\n<p>Highlights: No workplace injury and sickness incident, Perfect  Score in Customer Care, With 5 positive customer feedbacks, Perfect Score in Compliance to Policies under Major Offense. </p>\n\n<strong><p>For the Nursing Category (Special Area): Team 17 composing OPD, MOR, MIS, CWOC, HM, CFS2, CFC, TO, LTO, DAF, and WC/ENCODERS ranked as 1st place with the average rating of 68%. </p></strong>\n<p>Highlights: No Undertime, No Workplace Injury or Accident,  Perfect Score in Customer Care, No sickness Incidence, Perfect Score in Phone Courtesy, Perfect Score in Social Responsibility, Perfect Score for both Minor and Major Offenses in Compliance to hospital policies. </p>\n\n<p>The awards were given by Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr., President and Chairman of the Board; Engr. Oscar A. Tuason, Hospital Administrator; and Mrs. Bettina Veloso, Comptroller. </p>\n\n<strong><p>Congratulations to all the winners!!</p></strong>\n\n\n\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\n    <hr />\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\n    <br />\n	<div id=\"links\">\n            \n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/1.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\" alt=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/1.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/2.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\" alt=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/2.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/3.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\" alt=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/3.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/4.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\" alt=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/4.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/5.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\" alt=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/5.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div> \n			  <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/6.jpg\" data-gallery title=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\" alt=\"TEAM REWARS WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF JANUARY 2017\">\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/feb/feb17/6.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\n                </a>                \n            </div>\n			  \n			\n  <div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n	</div>                    \n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#fff;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CDUHOfficial/photos/?tab=album&album_id=1735052003435338\">Click here for more Photos...</a>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div><br /><br />', 'gallery/feb/feb17/6.jpg'),
(37, 'MEDICAL MISSION APRIL 2017', '2017-04-28', 'Admin / HR', '<strong><p>MEDICAL MISSION APRIL 2017</p></strong>\r\n<p>\r\n    A Strong Desire to help others less fortunate people, Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital organized a yearly Medical Mission held last April 22, 2017 at San Roque Parish, Subangdaku Mandaue City. This project is line with the 77th Birthday celebration of the President and Chairman of the Board of Cebu Doc Group, Dr. Potenciano V. Larrazabal, Jr.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    More than 500 patients were benefited and given Free Services range from Medical and Pediatric consultations to dental cleaning and tooth extraction, eye examination, and circumcision.  Check-up for medical were given to 125 adults and 120 for Pediatrics. 372 recipients also received prescription medicines and 114 were given reading glasses for free; 102 patients for ECG Test and 306 patients for FREE CBS and Blood Typing. Free snacks were also given to all the patients.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    The medical mission was carried out by Cebu Doctors’ University Hospital (CDUH) Administrators and partners from the different drug companies. Manpower services were provided by the volunteer staff from CDUH and volunteers from San Roque Parish, Subangdaku, Mandaue City. Doctors, Interns, Optometrists, Dentist, Surgeons, Student Nurses, Pharmacy Staff, Social Workers, and Admin Staff also volunteered the activity. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    Serving people is one way of showing our love and care. It is not how much we give, but how much love we put into giving. \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<strong><p>\r\n    “WE LEAD TO SERVE AND WE SERVE SO THAT OTHERS MAY LIVE.\"\r\n</p></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><p>\r\n    #CDUHCARES\r\n</p></strong>\r\n\r\n<div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"gallery\">\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <h5>Photo Gallery</h5>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <div id=\"links\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/1.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\" alt=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/1.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n              <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/2.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\" alt=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/2.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n              <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/3.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\" alt=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/3.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n              <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/4.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\" alt=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/4.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n              <div class=\"col-sm-3\">\r\n                <a href=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/5.JPG\" data-gallery title=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\" alt=\"WE LEAD TO SERVE: THE MEDICAL MISSION PROGRAM 2017\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../../images/gallery/april2017/5.JPG\" class=\"img-responsive thumbnail\"/>\r\n                </a>                \r\n            </div> \r\n              <