(43, 'TEAM REWARD WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF SEPTEMBER 2017\r\n', '2017-10-30', 'Admin / HR', '<strong><p>TEAM REWARD WINNERS FOR THE MONTH OF SEPTEMBER 2017</p></strong>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>A. NON-NURSING CATEGORY:</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 11</b> composing <b>Laboratory Group 1</b> ranked <b>1st place</b> as they got the overall rating of <b>85.52%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 7</b> composing <b>Business Office 3</b> ranked <b>2nd place</b> with the overall rating of <b>84.56%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 13</b> composing <b>Pharmacy</b> ranked as <b>3rd place</b> with the overall rating of <b>77.99%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>B. NURSING CATEGORY (SPECIAL AREA)</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 19</b> composing <b>PICU/RICU</b> ranked <b>1st place</b> as they got the overall rating of <b>80.97%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 21</b> composing <b>Delivery Room/Nursery</b> ranked <b>2nd place</b> with the overall rating of <b>76.73%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 17</b> composing <b>OPD, MOR, MIS, CWOC & HM</b> ranked <b>3nd place</b> with the overall rating of <b>76.20%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <strong>C. NURSING CATEGORY (SPECIAL AREA)</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 26</b> composing <b>3A & 5B Stations</b> ranked <b>1st place</b> as they got the overall rating of <b>69.11%.</b>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>HALL OF FAMER</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <b>Team 6</b> composing <b>Business Office 2</b> and <b>Team 5</b> composing <b>Business Office 1</b> qualifies for the category as they reach the average rating required\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    The awards were given by <b>Dr. Potenciano S.D. Larrazabal, III</b> (Medical Director),\r\n    <b>Engr. Oscar A. Tuason</b> (Hospital Administrator), and <b>Mrs. Betty Anne Veloso</b> (Comptroller).\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    It was also well attended by the Admin Circle Heads.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    <st