(7, '2019-04-15', 'thumbnail/dentalinstitute.jpg', 'dental/3-2000x1328-800x531.jpg', 'cebudoc-opens-new-dental-institute', 'cebu doctors hospital, dental institute, Dr. Imelda P. Montuerto, dental wellness', 'CebuDoc opens New Dental Institute', 'The country’s most outstanding hospital for Level III, Cebu Doctors University Hospital, launches its newest Dental Institute to be among its growing wellness brands.\r\n', '    <section class=\"mbr-section article content1 cid-content-body\" id=\"content1-mt\">\r\n    \r\n\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\r\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style display-7\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    The country’s most outstanding hospital for Level III, Cebu Doctors University Hospital, launches its newest Dental Institute to be among its growing wellness brands.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					CebuDoc Dental Institute offers a comprehensive and advanced array of dental health services such as General Dentistry, Preventive Dentistry, Dental Diagnostic Laboratory Services, Orthodontics, Endodontics, Cosmetic Dentistry, Prosthodontics, Pediatric Dentistry, TMD Management, Periodontics, Dental Implants, and Oral Maxillofacial Surgery.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					The newly built dental facility is part of the developing Wellness Complex situated in the Medical Arts Building 2 of Cebu Doctors University Hospital. It is the second center opened since Wellness Complex has been introduced last year through the opening of Center for Aesthetics and Laser.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					“We have been investing to change the healthcare system in CebuDoc Group such as which we want to provide a holistic type of care and this is part of it, the dental healthcare system,” said CebuDoc Group’s President and Chairman, Dr. Potenciano “Yong” Larrazabal, III.\r\n\r\n                </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"mbr-section article content1 cid-content-body\" id=\"content1-mt\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style display-7\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\">Authority in Dental Health</h2>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    This latest wellness brand of CebuDoc boasts authority in the dental health profession having gathered the most reputable and top-caliber dentists in the region headed by its chairman, Dr. Imelda P. Montuerto who is also the current Dean of Cebu Doctors University College of Dentistry.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					“Here in our dental center, we made sure that all our staff is very compassionate that will attend to your every need. We’ve chosen and we’ve got top-notch Dentists all under one roof – they are very known and well respected in their respective fields of dentistry”, Dr. Larrazabal emphasized.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					Joining the team are Dr. Charles P. Sia who specializes in Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery, Dr. Andrea A. Arancillo in Periodontics & Implant Dentistry, Dr. Sandra G. Lavastilla and Dr. Zonnette M. Enso in Endodontics, Dr. Larissa Ann A. Lim in Pediatric Dentistry, Dr. Joanna Bless T. Yap in Orthodontics, and Dr. Judy Melissa L. Vesuña and Dr. Jestoni D. Lagare in General Dentistry.\r\n                </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"mbr-section article content1 cid-content-body\" id=\"content1-mt\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style display-7\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\">Leader in Innovation</h2>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Known for its innovative brands, CebuDoc Dental Institute is equipped with the latest technology in Dental Wellness that will make the patient experience more reliable and digitally integrated.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					“We are known to innovate. Whatever is new in the industry, we provide. Our dental center has a CBCT (Cone Beam Computed Tomography) or CT-Scan for Dentists, it has a digitalized X-Ray System, we have 3 dental chairs, and one operating room”, Dr. Larrazabal added.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					As if technological innovation is not enough, CebuDoc Dental Institute aims to revolutionalize Dental Health profession in the region as it will soon offer Residency Training program for Dentists who wish to specialize in their practice.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					“It will not only be an ordinary dental clinic because eventually we will be offering residency program in the different dental specializations”, CebuDoc Dental Institute Chairman, Dr. Imelda Montuerto, said.\r\n\r\n                </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"mbr-section article content1 cid-content-body\" id=\"content1-mt\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 col-md-8 mbr-fonts-style display-7\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"pb-3 mbr-fonts-style display-5\">Dental Health for all Cebuanos</h2>\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Keeping its commitment, to deliver high quality healthcare to the Filipinos especially Cebuanos, CebuDoc Dental Institute makes sure that its dental services will reach everyone who needs it.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					“For me, the highest quality of dental care is making the patients happy with the service that we have at a very affordable cost. Everyone is welcome. CebuDoc has been known to cater to everyone without discrimination”, Dr. Montuerto added.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					To help reach more Cebuanos of all ages, CebuDoc partnered with Binibining Cebu 2018 Queens to be the official Wellness Ambassadors hoping to inspire more to take care not just their dental health but their total well-being.<br><br>\r\n\r\n					“Having healthy teeth can really boost someone’s confidence especially when dealing with people. You get to talk and smile a lot. It brings out the best of your personality and, for me, that is enough reason why people should take care of their teeth”, Binibing Cebu 2018 Steffi Aberasturi concluded.\r\n                </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</section>', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div><!-- Filter --><!-- Gallery --><div class=\"mbr-gallery-row\"><div class=\"mbr-gallery-layout-default\"><div><div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-nj\" data-slide-to=\"0\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets/images/pressrelease/dental/1-1-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"Dental Institute\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-nj\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets/images/pressrelease/dental/2-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-nj\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets/images/pressrelease/dental/3-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-nj\" data-slide-to=\"3\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img src=\"../../../assets/images/pressrelease/dental/4-2000x1328-800x531.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"><span class=\"icon-focus\"></span></div></div><div class=\"mbr-gallery-item mbr-gallery-item--p1\" data-video-url=\"false\" data-tags=\"Animated\"><div href=\"#lb-gallery1-nj\" data-slide-to=\"4\" data-to