(1, 'The Outstanding Teams for the Month of August have been recognized!', 'Boosting the best of August. The winners for this month is always up for the challenge. Close call, but all teams performed well!', '<strong>Winners for the Non-Nursing Category:</strong>\r\n              <div>Team 5 composing Business Office 1 ranked 1st place as they got the average rate of 85.25%.</div>\r\n              <div>Team 6 composing Business Office 2 ranked 2nd place as they got the average rate of 85.01%.</div>\r\n              <div>Team 8 composing Dietary ranked 3rd Place as they got the average rate of 81.53%.</div>\r\n            <br>\r\n              <div><strong>Hall of Fame:</strong></div>\r\n              <div>Team 13 composing Pharmacy ranked 1st place as they got the average rate of 84.77%.</div>\r\n              <div>Team 7 composing Business Office 3 ranked 2nd place as they got the average rate of 83.65%.</div>\r\n            <br>\r\n              <div><strong>Winners for the Nursing Category (Non-Special Area):</strong></div>\r\n              <div>Team 24 composing 2C ranked 1st place as they got the average rate of 84.84%.</div>\r\n            <br>\r\n              <div><strong>Hall of Fame:</strong></div>\r\n              <div>Team 26 composing 3A and 5B Stations ranked 1st place as they got the average rate of 76.11%.</div>\r\n              <div>Team 29 composing 5A Station ranked 2nd place as they got the average rate of 75.89%.</div>\r\n              <div>Team 24 composing 2C Station ranked 3rd Place as they got the average rate of 72.79%.</div>\r\n              <br>\r\n              <div><strong>Winners for the Nursing Category (Special Area):</strong></div>\r\n            <br>\r\n              <div><strong>Hall of Fame:</strong></div>\r\n              <div>Team 17 composing OPD, MOR, MIS, CWOC &amp; HM ranked 1st place as they got the average rate of 84.01%.</div>\r\n              <div>Team 21 composing Delivery and Nursery Units ranked 2nd place as they got