INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `content`) VALUES
(1, '<style>\r\n	.bg-testimonials{\r\n		background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n		max-width: 100%;\r\n		border-radius: 10px;\r\n		padding-top: 15px;\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>Thank you for the caring nurses assigned to me, who not only showed concern, warmth and caring but were very polite, Angz, Jam and Jess. I also want to thank the loud-mouthed guys in the recovery room who wouldn’t allow me to drift to sleep, the dietary guys who brought the food, the cleaning staff and everyone else in Cebu Doctors, thank you for taking care of me and making me feel like a pricess</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>MS. BELLE GRANDEA</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Cebu Daily News</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\"><q>Tell it to Belle </q>Section</font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(2, '<style>\r\n	.bg-testimonials{\r\n		background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n		max-width: 100%;\r\n		border-radius: 10px;\r\n		padding-top: 15px;\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>I’d like to commend all the nurses who helped assisted me during my stay because they were all genuine in rendering their services to me as a patient. And all other hospital staff from PT Department,\r\nI thank you so much and I’ll never forget all of you. God Bless you all and your family always and forever.</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>MR. REYNALDO REY ALVAREZ</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Rehab Patient</font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(3, '<style>\r\n	.bg-testimonials{\r\n		background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n		max-width: 100%;\r\n		border-radius: 10px;\r\n		padding-top: 15px;\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>In my personal experiences, I do appreciate the services Cebu Doctors’ Hospital has.. Been to \r\nDifferent hospitals in Cebu due to my own illness the past years and yet my family still goes back\r\nand choose to be at Cebu Doc. God Bless!\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>MS. JESSICA NUNEZ</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Facebook Offical Page</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Reviewed 5 stars</font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(4, '<style>\r\n	.bg-testimonials{\r\n		background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n		max-width: 100%;\r\n		border-radius: 10px;\r\n		padding-top: 15px;\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>Having an offer on such prestigious hospital is a great help to those who are not well-off but likes to be catered with the best. Thank you OPD-CDUH for the opportunity.\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>OPD PATIENT</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(5, '<style>\r\n	.bg-testimonials{\r\n		background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n		max-width: 100%;\r\n		border-radius: 10px;\r\n		padding-top: 15px;\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>We are loyal to CDUH because we know the competence of its manpower and service. Its cleanliness is also consistent and the facilities are state-of-the-art. Kudos to all CDUH doctors, nurses and staff for their professionalism and excellent competence. We will forever be thankful for your service and quality healthcare.\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>MR. JAZER JAMES ATADERO</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Facebook Official Page</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Reviewed 5 stars</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(6, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>So far among all hospitals here in Cebu, CDUH is the best in terms of Doctors assistance to the patient. And the availability of the facilities and laboratory equipment. Surely, you\'re in good hands with Cebu Doctors.\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>MR. KHULAS KHO</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Facebook Official Page</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Reviewed 5 stars</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(7, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>\r\nExcellent in attending patient\'s need, Center for Cancer is comfortable to stay in for a while. The nurses are all approachable and friendly as well. Thankful to God we have this center to help people\'s health condition. More Power!\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Center for Cancer Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(8, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>\r\nMy little girl was provided with the best care from ER services down to when we transferred to our room. Best facilities with modern equipment available. For the discharge time, I did not encounter any issues from Philhealth claims down to cashier for final settlement of bill. Thank you CDUH!\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>JERALYN-ROWEL ALUNAN</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Facebook Official Page</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Reviewed 5 stars</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(9, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>They are very good in entertaining their patients and they explain and try to make the patient understand the situation. They make their patient and watcher fell comfortable so we\'re very thankful for all the care that they give us. Thank you and God Bles!\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Endoscopy Unit Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(10, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>I really like this hospital. I went there yesterday in the E.R. The staffs, nurses and doctors are very friendly and they\'re going to take care of you immediately. Keep it up! I love Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital. That\'s why our family choose this hospital.\r\n</q> \r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Ms. Anz Vancougn</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Facebook Official Page</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Reviewed 5 stars</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(11, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>The Love and care you extended to your patients are much appreciated\r\n</q>.\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Renal Intensive Care Unit Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Customer Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(12, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>The service is excellent. The room is clean and well-ventilated. Nurses are well-mannered and kind. Keep up the good work.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Minor Operating Room Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Customer Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(13, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n<q>\r\n    Being a nurse, it is hard when you become the patient. Last December, I had a surgery but I never informed any of the staff that I was a nurse and yes, the hospital services did not disappoint me at all. Nurses were timely in giving out meds and they were all courteous when they entered the room. The residents were most of the time in a hurry but still the time to explain was there.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Mr. Neil Bertulfo</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Google Reviews</font><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Rated 4 stars</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n'),
(14, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    They give us the best quality nursing care that we need. The facility of the hospital is good and also the workers of this hospital are well accommodating. God Bless all of you!\r\n</q>.\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Endoscopy Unit Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n'),
(16, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    Cebu Doctors\' University Hospital was amongst the best hospital in the Philippines. The\r\nRespected Medical Staffs & Consultants are good hearted, able to save life..A Pro Life Hospital\r\n</q>.\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Ms. Aida De Castro</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Facebook Official Page</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n'),
(17, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    Aside of those very approachable nurses, staff and doctors, the hospital was so clean and have a convenient odor. Stay the same thing to all the patients. Thank you very much.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>Minor OR Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n'),
(18, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    As a whole CDUH OPD is excellent in their service. I\'m proud to recommend them to my friends.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>OPD Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n'),
(19, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    To all the doctors and nurses, thank you for serving us and thank you too for all the staff in Cebu Doctors. We hope you will not change your good attitudes and God Speed.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>ER Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(20, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    I am very impressed to all attendants that they serve better to us. I hope they will continue serving better to poor people in appreciative way.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>OPD Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>'),
(21, '<style>\r\n    .bg-testimonials{\r\n        background-color: #b3d1ff;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n        border-radius: 10px;\r\n        padding-top: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"container bg-testimonials\">\r\n\r\n<q>\r\n    Very efficient nurses! Kudos! They are very smiling and I find it necessary in building rapport. They do their job well and they showed confidence in performing any procedures thus making me less anxious. Thank you so much for your world class care. I could not pick one best nurse because the team seems well calibrated in providing services.\r\n</q>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"right\"><strong>- <em>3A Station Patient</em></strong><br>\r\n<font size=\"2\">Source: Random Satisfaction Survey</font>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr>\r\n');
